(2, 499, 'Emily Collins', 'edcollins25@gmail.com', '', '204.15.160.250', '2013-04-03 13:45:26', '2013-04-03 13:45:26', 'Such a great product recommendation. I purchased the Nars Satin Lip Pencil in Lodhi and I cannot stop wearing it, it stays on all day long and is such a great spring daytime color. Plus you don''t need a lip liner and if you exfoliate your lips first and you don''t even need a gloss on top (though using a little lip balm is nice to lock in the moisture). Thanks Sarah! \n\nBisous! \nxx', 0, '1', '', '', 0, 0),
