(495, 1, '2013-02-21 20:26:03', '2013-02-21 20:26:03', '<p class="alignnone size-full wp-image-193">Dreamtown! Pun intended. Yesterday + today I teamed up with <a href="http://www.essence.eu/us/home.html" target="_blank">Essence Cosmetics</a> for desksides, [in my case, industry talk for visiting the fabulous beauty editors in NYC...]. If you aren''t familiar with the Essence, they are an incredible value brand out of Germany. If you are in the USA check out <a href="http://search.ulta.com/search?p=Q&amp;lbc=ulta&amp;uid=657721258&amp;ts=custom&amp;w=essence%20makeup&amp;method=and&amp;userid=Guest&amp;view=grid&amp;isort=date&amp;modaf=r:brand:essence" target="_blank">Ulta Beauty,</a> all you Canadians, Essence is readily available at Shoppers Drug Mart. I am a big fan of the line +Â  unlike most value brands, Essence has saturated color + pigment, staying power, + on trend products.</p>\r\n<!--more-->Â The days consisted of running between the Time+Life building, Conde Nast, Hearst, + more. It was so much fun to connect with the editors! Be sure to check out Essence''s Stays No Matter What collection launching in the next two weeks. My favorite: Stays No Matter What eye pencil in black. This Spring, get into it! S.\r\n<p class="alignnone size-full wp-image-193"><a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/3.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-191" alt="3" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/3.jpg" width="1188" height="1701" /></a> <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/photo-2.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-192" alt="photo 2" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/photo-2.jpg" width="2448" height="3264" /></a></p>', 'Desksides, the Essence of...', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'desksides-the-essence-of', '', '', '2015-01-28 07:03:24', '2015-01-28 07:03:24', '', 0, 'http://sarahappleby.com/blog/?p=190', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(496, 1, '2013-02-19 14:52:13', '2013-02-19 14:52:13', 'I am fresh off the long haul from MEL&gt;AKL&gt;LAX&gt;NYC, where I spent a few weeks both working + playing [more to come..]. When you are in the air, with no fresh air for that length of time, you need a great skincare regimen. It makes all the difference. I am not a huge fan of wearing makeup when I travel, less is more- your skin will thank you...<!--more-->\r\n\r\n<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/photo-2-1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-223" alt="photo 2-1" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/photo-2-1.jpg" width="720" height="720" /></a> <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/photo.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-224" alt="photo" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/photo.jpg" width="827" height="827" /></a><!--more-->When I am up, up, + away: I use my <a href="http://www.skyniceland.com/product-23-nordic-skin-peel" target="_blank">Skyn Nordic Skin Peel</a>, they are pads that have Lactic acid, a gentle AHA (alpha hydroxy acid) derived from corn sugar, which helps exfoliate the skin. I leave that for half an hour or so + then follow up with the Amore Pacific <a href="http://us.amorepacific.com/en/product/MOISTURE_BOUND_Skin_Energy_Hydration_Delivery_System" target="_blank">Moisture Bound Skin Energy Hydration Delivery System</a>, spraying all over my face. I moisturize with <a href="http://us.caudalie.com/moisturizing-sorbet.html?gclid=CLb0mJL59LUCFYje4AodrR8AHw" target="_blank">Caudalie Moisturizing Sorbet</a> all over the face- use liberally! + <a href="http://us.caudalie.com/premier-cru-the-eye-cream-1.html" target="_blank">Caudalie Premier Cru The Eye Cream</a> around the eyes [be gentle!]. For the lips, <a href="http://us.nuxe.com/en/reve-de-miel-ultra-nourishing-lip-balm-160/reve-de-miel" target="_blank">Reve de Miel Lip Balm</a>, it has a lovely creamy, matte texture + a nice subtle flavor. If I have any spots, or need a little brightening under the eyes, I will apply a touch of<a href="http://www.lauramercier.com/store/shop/Concealers_Secret%20Concealer_prod220006" target="_blank"> Laura Mercier Secret Concealer</a>, medium coverage + super creamy texture.\r\n\r\nThroughout the flights, along with drinking copious amounts of water, I try to stay away from the airplane food which is packed with unnecessary sodium + will opt for packing a sandwich or salad if available.\r\n\r\nIt''s worth it to take the extra time to make sure your body + skin are all taken care of, upon landing you will feel the difference + be ready for an adventure!\r\n\r\nHappy hydrated travels!\r\n\r\nS.', 'Planes Trains + Beauty Mobiles', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'planes-trains-beauty-mobiles', '', '', '2015-01-28 07:05:13', '2015-01-28 07:05:13', '', 0, 'http://sarahappleby.com/blog/?p=221', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(497, 1, '2013-02-26 17:53:49', '2013-02-26 17:53:49', ' Tonite I had the pleasure of attending an amazing event at the Plaza Hotel, thrown by French skincare line, Caudalie [they run the beautiful spa there]. If you know me well, you have already heard my continuous praises for Mathilde + Bertrand, the husband + wife power duo behind the line. The products are absolutely delicious. <!--more--><a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/photo-2-2.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-235" alt="photo 2-2" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/photo-2-2.jpg" width="2283" height="3044" /></a> <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/photo-3.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-236" alt="photo 3" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/photo-3.jpg" width="2372" height="3162" /></a>It all began on their family vineyard in Bordeaux, France- as if that is not dreamy enough! It is the perfect fit for me, as I have so much love for France, Parisian culture, Wine + Skincare! It was an evening of Vino [off of the family''s vineyard <a href="http://www.smith-haut-lafitte.com/en/" target="_blank">Chateau Smith Haut Lafitte</a>], education on the new launches of skincare [specifically the newly formulated <a href="http://us.caudalie.com/products-best-sellers/collections/vinosource.html?utm_source=Google&amp;utm_medium=cpc&amp;utm_term=vinosource%20caudalie&amp;utm_content=Skincare&amp;utm_campaign=Vinosource&amp;gclid=CM2LwKqc9bUCFVKf4AodREMAsw" target="_blank">Vinosource line</a>] + even a quick facial, thanks Oxsana!\r\n\r\nMy kit, as well as my personal cabinet is stocked with their products, I can''t live without. I hope to be back to the spa sooner than later, in the meantime I am doing my own ''Vinotherapie''- out of the tube + glass! S.', 'Once Upon a Vine...', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'once-upon-a-vine', '', '', '2015-01-28 07:06:16', '2015-01-28 07:06:16', '', 0, 'http://sarahappleby.com/blog/?p=233', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(498, 1, '2013-02-27 11:04:49', '2013-02-27 11:04:49', '<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/aliceweb41.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-304" alt="aliceweb4" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/aliceweb41.jpg" width="675" height="450" /></a>I recently had the opportunity to work with actress/model <a href="http://www.imdb.com/name/nm3640535/">Alice Callahan</a> [Gossip Girl/Law+Order etc] on a shoot for some new sparkly press photos. She is a natural beauty. For makeup, I kept it fresh + clean: dewy skin + textured lashes. Then popped a matte red lip, so classic. For hair, it was a play on her natural waves, adding a little more with a big barrel iron + putting in lots of salt spray, + then we threw it up in a top knot later in the eve...<!--more--><a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/aliceweb2.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-297" alt="aliceweb2" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/aliceweb2.jpg" width="675" height="450" /></a> <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/aliceweb3.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-298" alt="aliceweb3" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/aliceweb3.jpg" width="675" height="450" /></a>\n\nIsn''t she just lovely. Had so much fun running around with the crew in Dumbo that afternoon! Photos by <a href="http://philipanema.com/" target="_blank">Phil Anema</a> / Styling by <a href="http://morgangibbons.com/" target="_blank">Morgan Gibbons</a>\n\nS.', 'A Lovely Alice', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'a-lovely-alice', '', '', '2013-02-27 11:04:49', '2013-02-27 11:04:49', '', 0, 'http://sarahappleby.com/blog/?p=242', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(499, 1, '2013-03-07 18:58:08', '2013-03-07 18:58:08', 'Just got home from a fun event at the NARS boutique on Bleecker street in the West Village. Being that it is just blocks from my old apartment, although wet + rainy, I love strolling that neighborhood + was happy to venture over that way to get inspired with NARS newness...<!--more-->\r\n\r\n<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-251" alt="photo 2" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/photo-21.jpg" width="2362" height="1575" /> <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/photo-31.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-252" alt="photo 3" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/photo-31.jpg" width="2176" height="3263" /></a> <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/photo-4.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-253" alt="photo 4" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/photo-4.jpg" width="2043" height="3064" /></a>NARS has just launched the new <a href="http://www.narscosmetics.com/the-latest/collections/newest-collections-from-nars/satin-lip-pencil-collection" target="_blank">Satin Lip Pencil</a> in 13 gorgeous shades. I am all about a lip, all the time. While sipping on Champagne, I perused the tiny boutique, running into both friends + peers. The new Lip Pencil is creamy in texture with full coverage [high impact color!] + the classic Satin finish. It gives me the coverage + saturation that I want in a lip pencil with a natural texture to finish. These are amazing on their own or topped off with a gloss. I picked up Floralies, Isola Bella, Rikugien, Hyde Park + Palais Royal.I have a feeling I will be heading back that way to pick up the rest of the shades very soon... S.', 'Champagne/ Satin Lips', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'drinking-champagne-with-satin-lips', '', '', '2015-01-28 07:01:34', '2015-01-28 07:01:34', '', 0, 'http://sarahappleby.com/blog/?p=249', 0, 'post', '', 1),
(500, 1, '2013-03-14 12:30:34', '2013-03-14 12:30:34', 'This compilation has been a long time coming... I am blessed to work with some of the most talented musicians in the world [Lykke Li, Duran Duran, Sleigh Bells, Mark Ronson + more]. I love it. There is something about working with other artists + being with them in such an intimate space [often doing vocal warm up] while I am getting them ready that is so liberating! Inspiring! I have such fun memories of applying makeup to Lykke Li while she''s singing a Stevie Nicks song, amazing. Or jushing [it''s in the urban dictionary!] Simon Le Bon''s hair while he belts out Girl Panic ! Here is a video reel that I put together housing some of my very favorite moments. Song on the reel is done by my dear friend [grew up with this one!] Megan James, Purity Ring. Get into it. ENJOY X\r\n\r\nhttps://vimeo.com/61669529', 'Reeling: Music Muses', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'reeling-music-muses', '', '', '2015-01-28 07:08:48', '2015-01-28 07:08:48', '', 0, 'http://sarahappleby.com/blog/?p=258', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(501, 1, '2013-02-28 17:10:59', '2013-02-28 17:10:59', 'Spending some playtime on the beaches in + around Melbourne, Australia. Diamond Bay, Moggs Creek, Lorne etc. They are all stunning. I love taking the time to dig in the sand, explore the beachscape + make my own adventure. I am always in awe at the range of texture + color: shells, sandstone [Aus has a lot of this!], seaglass, clay, rocks, etc...<!--more--> <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/2mar5.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-268" alt="2mar5" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/2mar5.jpg" width="2448" height="1632" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/3mar5.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-269" alt="3mar5" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/3mar5.jpg" width="2392" height="1595" /></a> <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/4mar5.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-270" alt="4mar5" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/4mar5.jpg" width="1287" height="858" /></a>The colors are dreamy. It is no wonder why so many makeup lines get their collections from beaches, both textures + colors. I look at the beach + see eyeshadow palettes! It is as if the ocean is decorated with all of these lovely accessories. The beach is one of my favorite places to be, but not for too long, the concrete jungle has my heart.', 'Australia/ Beach DÃ©cor', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'australia-beach-decor', '', '', '2015-01-28 07:06:36', '2015-01-28 07:06:36', '', 0, 'http://sarahappleby.com/blog/?p=266', 0, 'post', '', 1),
(502, 1, '2013-03-05 22:19:32', '2013-03-05 22:19:32', 'The Oscars, we are all bombarded with who''s hot + who''s not on the Red Carpet... I am happy to hand out my opinion to whomever asks! <a href="http://oribe.com/" target="_blank">Oribe</a>, one of my very favorite hair care brands, reached out to me to chat about some of the trends we were seeing... <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-311" alt="Screen shot 2013-03-11 at 2.27.47 PM" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Screen-shot-2013-03-11-at-2.27.47-PM.png" width="803" height="566" /></a>\r\n\r\nThe Nude Lips + Highlighted Inner Rim were two of the biggest trends... A welcomed change up from past seasons. Classic, beautiful, effortless.', 'Oribe/ Oscar Trend Review', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'oribe-oscar-trend-review', '', '', '2015-01-28 07:03:02', '2015-01-28 07:03:02', '', 0, 'http://sarahappleby.com/blog/?p=309', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(503, 1, '2013-03-13 17:06:02', '2013-03-13 17:06:02', '<p style="text-align: center;">There were so many incredible beauty moments throughout NY, MIL, LDN, PAR for Autumn/Winter 2013. Here are a few of my favorite makeup looks, all designed by the best makeup artists in the world. Top L to Bottom R. Kenzo/AaronDeMay [Love the glossy texturedlid/unbalanced smoky eye] â€¢ Giorgio Armani/LindaCantello [Beautiful Matte skin/always a fan of inner nose+brow contour] â€¢ Lanvin/PatMcGrath [obsessed with the graphic eye/simple with blacks+greys/no brow = love] â€¢ Jean Paul Gaultier/LloydSimmons [all for the severe brow! + with nothing else, perfect] â€¢ Givenchy/PatMcGrath [pretty floral coloring on the eyes very autumn, with highlighted inner rim] â€¢Â  Celine/DickPage [Phoebe+Dick can do no wrong, flawless skin with a bronzer in blush placement, natural but a statement ]. Feeling inspired!</p>', 'Fashion Week A/W 2013: Inspiration', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'fashion-week-aw-2013-inspiration', '', '', '2015-01-28 07:01:13', '2015-01-28 07:01:13', '', 0, 'http://sarahappleby.com/blog/?p=324', 0, 'post', '', 0),
