(505, 1, '2013-03-25 11:57:36', '2013-03-25 11:57:36', 'I love my weekends. Living in Brooklyn, one of my favorite things to do is spend time shopping at my local farmers market. Stocking up on freshness to carry me through the week with copious amounts of green juices + smoothies. <!--more-->\r\n\r\nReasons this is a priority:\r\n\r\nâ€¢ Getting to know the farmers + supporting local agriculture\r\n\r\nâ€¢ Organic meats/produce are significantly less expensive\r\n\r\nâ€¢ You will eat seasonally! Produce is going to be fresh + ripe...\r\n\r\nâ€¢ The markets are beautiful! The colors of fresh flowers, fruit, veggies- so pretty + I need that fix this time of year while the trees + parks are so bare. <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/photo-32.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-355" alt="photo 3" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/photo-32.jpg" width="2840" height="2130" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/photo-22.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-354" alt="photo 2" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/photo-22.jpg" width="2746" height="2060" /></a>\r\n\r\nAs the Winter is early over, the variety of goods available is slimmer than the summer months. Yesterday I stocked up on greens [kale, spinach, collard], carrots, squash, onions, garlic, apples, + fresh flowers of course!\r\n\r\n+ Now I juice. This morning''s concoction:Â 5 stems of kale / 2 carrots / chunk of fresh ginger / 1 honey crisp apple / squeeze of fresh lemon <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/photo2.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-359" alt="photo" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/photo2.jpg" width="2584" height="1938" /></a>\r\n\r\nI know when the nutrition [clean foods/juices] in our diet changes for the better, the skin is one of the first places we will see results. Here''s to delicious green juice + a glowy canvas to work our beauty on. Get into it!', 'Markets  +  Juicing/ For your skin''s sake', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'markets-juicing-for-your-skins-sake', '', '', '2015-01-28 07:00:45', '2015-01-28 07:00:45', '', 0, 'http://sarahappleby.com/blog/?p=352', 0, 'post', '', 5),
(506, 1, '2013-03-29 14:17:27', '2013-03-29 14:17:27', 'One of my favorite musicians to work with; Sleigh Bells. Alexis Krauss is such a bombshell. I love how she emotes darkness + has such an edge about her, yet is one of the loveliest gals I have ever worked with. Derek is amazing too + quirky + neurotic + crazy talented on so many levels. His 90''s playlists blow my mind. SO SO good. Â  <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/sb3.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-367" alt="SPIN-MARAPR-COVER-DP9.indd" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/sb3.jpg" width="650" height="449" /></a><!--more-->\r\n\r\nAlong with press events, we have shot for Spin, Clash, Paper + more. Can we also talk about their music. I am such a fan. <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/SB.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-369" alt="SB" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/SB.jpg" width="650" height="946" /></a><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-368" alt="sb2" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/sb2.jpg" width="650" height="508" /><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-366" alt="sb4" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/sb4.jpg" width="650" height="951" />\r\n\r\nIt''s a lot of eyeliner, structured brows + plump lips. Alexis'' hair is gorgeous, silky, healthy + easy to work with. Love the black against her fair, flawless skin.Â  She can do no wrong.<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-371" alt="SBCLASH3" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/SBCLASH3.jpg" width="335" height="450" /><a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/SBCLASH2.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-373" alt="SBCLASH2" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/SBCLASH2.jpg" width="715" height="450" /></a><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-372" alt="SBCLASH