(556, 1, '2013-05-01 18:36:33', '2013-05-01 18:36:33', 'Yesterday worked with the amazing team from Beauty High, painting + creating two gals in pretty pastels. Oh! + We shot in the cutest candy shop, CuRious Candy by Cynthia Rowley. When on the UES, you must check out...\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\n<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/20130501-140220.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full" alt="20130501-140220.jpg" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/20130501-140220.jpg" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/20130501-140339.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full" alt="20130501-140339.jpg" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/20130501-140339.jpg" /></a>I used Jurlique skincare on the girl to prep their skin, love the Radiance Serum, which really helps lock in moisture, giving you a glowy effect. Then used mainly cream color bases from MAC on their eyes + cheeks. Stila just launched Countless Color Pigments, such a beautiful range of colors, perfectly fitting for the concept of the shoot, I used to layer over the eyes. It was a day surrounded by the most delicious candy + colors, pastel hair (obsessed! Johnny styling + Zoe Wiepert coloring), + making beautiful images thanks to photographer Meghan McGarry. Can''t wait to see the final story! More from the shoot...\r\n\r\n<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/20130501-140459.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full" alt="20130501-140459.jpg" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/20130501-140459.jpg" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/20130501-140521.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full" alt="20130501-140521.jpg" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/20130501-140521.jpg" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/20130501-140540.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full" alt="20130501-140540.jpg" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/20130501-140540.jpg" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/20130501-140558.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full" alt="20130501-140558.jpg" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/20130501-140558.jpg" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/20130501-140614.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full" alt="20130501-140614.jpg" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/20130501-140614.jpg" /></a>\r\n\r\n+ Happy May! Seems I should be headed to the nearest salon for some cotton candy colored hair....', 'Behind the Scenes/ Pastel Dreaming', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'behind-the-scenes-pastel-dreaming', '', '', '2015-01-28 06:21:51', '2015-01-28 06:21:51', '', 0, 'http://sarahappleby.com/blog/?p=556', 0, 'post', '', 1);
