ize-full wp-image-793" alt="harbourislandbeauty13" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/harbourislandbeauty131.jpg" width="3008" height="2256" /></a>The beaches in Harbour Island are picturesque, the people are lovely + I have every reason to head back that way, I have so much more to discover. X', 'A Photo Diary: Harbour Island, Bahamas', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'a-photo-diary-harbour-island-bahamas', '', '', '2015-01-28 06:07:52', '2015-01-28 06:07:52', '', 0, 'http://sarahappleby.com/blog/?p=778', 0, 'post', '', 2),
(805, 1, '2013-06-17 09:00:00', '2013-06-17 09:00:00', 'Summertime calls for much time out in the sun: whether you''re at the beach, a backyard barbecue, out for a bike ride or sitting on your fire escape, it''s important to take every precaution protecting your skin from the harsh rays. We have all seen + heard the many ways sun can damage your skin. Sunscreen + Sunblock + Shade- your best bet to avoiding burns, skin spots + even skin cancer. Here are my favorite go to products this summer season...<!--more-->\r\n\r\nâ€¢<a href="http://www.letan.com.au/product/5661/coconut-30~-lotion-125ml" target="_blank">LeTan Coconut Lotion SPF 30+</a>: my favorite sunscreen for the body. It''s made in Australia, non oily, smells like a coconut + works like a charm. I apply all over my body at least half an hour before I get into the sun + reapply every 2 hours. Definitely more if I am in + out of the water. I haven''t yet found a distributor in North America, however LeTan does offer <a href="http://www.letan.com.au/wheretobuy" target="_blank">international shipping</a>!\r\n\r\nâ€¢<a href="http://www.dermalogica.com/super-sensitive-shield-spf30/141,default,pd.html" target="_blank">Dermalogica Super Sensitive Shield SPF30+</a>: I use this on my face every morning. It''s lightweight, non oily + gives really nice coverage + protection. They use natural mineral sunscreens too. This also works really well under makeup. A staple for summer.\r\n\r\nâ€¢<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Aloe_vera" target="_blank">Aloe Vera Stems</a>: Of course after anytime out in the sun, the very best, natural way to cool + moisturize is to find some aloe vera plants. Cut them up + use generously all over your body. Aloe is known to be healing + cooling. This is a must for me, as I often deal with heat rash. I find this works wonders.\r\n\r\nThere you have it! My favorite ways to be sun smart, now get your inner mermaid on! X<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/letandermalogicaaloe1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-807" alt="letandermalogicaaloe1" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/letandermalogicaaloe1.jpg" width="2887" height="1925" /></a>', 'Fun in the Sun: skin safety first', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'fun-in-the-sun-skin-safety-first', '', '', '2015-01-28 06:06:15', '2015-01-28 06:06:15', '', 0, 'http://sarahappleby.com/blog/?p=805', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(813, 1, '2013-06-24 14:48:23', '2013-06-24 14:48:23', 'HOT TOWN SUMMER IN THE CITY! Here are my official summer sticks that will stay put in my bag over the next three sunny months...<!--more-->\r\n\r\n<em>SHISEIDO PERFECT ROUGE IN </em><a href="http://www.shiseido.com/perfect-rouge/9990000000039,en_US,pd.html&amp;cgid=makeup-lips-lipstick&amp;&amp;dwvar_9990000000039_color=00039_PK303" target="_blank"><em>PINK MESA PK 303</em></a>. The perfect cool baby pink lip. I love the texture of this stick, creamy + non drying.<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/sheiseidolipstick.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-815" alt="sheiseidolipstick" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/sheiseidolipstick.jpg" width="2140" height="1189" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<em>STILA STAY ALL DAY LIQUID LIPSTICK IN <a href="http://www.stilacosmetics.com/product/stay+all+day+liquid+lipstick.do?sortby=ourPicks" target="_blank">CARINA</a>.</em> I have raved about this product for ages. This orange/coral shade is a must have. The best complement to sun kissed skin. This liquid lipstick is easy to apply, color is bold, with a matte finish for the ultimate pop!<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/stilalip.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-816" alt="stilalip" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/stilalip.jpg" width="2144" height="1191" /></a><em></em>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<em>CHANEL ROUGE ALLURE LUMINOUS INTENSE LIP COLOR IN <a href="http://www.chanel.com/en_US/fragrance-beauty/Makeup-Lipstick-ROUGE-ALLURE-130969?sku=130985" target="_blank">104/ PASSION.</a> </em>This red is bold + has a hint of fuschia on the lips, a classic summer color for that statement lip. This one is limited so get it fast! Loving the texture, Chanel knows how to make the easiest wearing lipsticks.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/chanellip.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-817" alt="chanellip" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/chanellip.jpg" width="2144" height="1191" /></a><em></em>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<em>M</em><em>AC COSMETICS AMPLIFIED CREME LIPSTICK IN <a href="http://www.maccosmetics.com/product/shaded/168/310/Lipstick/index.tmpl" target="_blank">UP THE AMP</a>. </em>I love this lavender/violet creamy lipstick! Such a fun, playful poppy color, pretty on all skin tones.<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/chanellip.jpg">\r\n</a>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/macuptheamp.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-814" alt="macuptheamp" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/macuptheamp.jpg" width="2144" height="1191" /></a>\r\n\r\nI am a lip girl through + through. For a fun day at the beach, lake, or running around town. Flawless sunscreened skin + a lip will go far this summer!Â  X', 'Hello Summer! / Favorite Four Summer Lip Colors', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'hello-summer-favorite-four-summer-lip-colors', '', '', '2015-01-28 06:06:19', '2015-01-28 06:06:19', '', 0, 'http://sarahappleby.com/blog/?p=813', 0, 'post', '', 0);
