(1577, 1, '2014-07-15 02:44:07', '2014-07-15 02:44:07', 'Hello there. It''s been a long three months of blogless living working + playing. I have decided before the new website launches it is time to catch up! Summer has been busy + crazy + full of fun surprises! I am excited to share a little of what has been going on. Thank you for being patient with me + looking forward to hearing what you think of all the new musings... X', 'Hello there.', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'hello-there', '', '', '2015-01-27 11:34:21', '2015-01-27 11:34:21', '', 0, 'http://sarahappleby.com/blog/?p=1577', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(1581, 1, '2014-07-15 07:00:07', '2014-07-15 07:00:07', 'I recently worked with the lovely Birdy for her Refinery 29 piece, shot by Jens Ingvarsson. If you follow the blog you know how much I adore working with musicians, especially sweet souls like Birdy...<!--more-->\r\n\r\n<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/BIRDY_REFINERY_29_4.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1585" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/BIRDY_REFINERY_29_4.jpg" alt="BIRDY_REFINERY_29_4" width="1066" height="1600" /></a>Â <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/BIRDY_REFINERY_29_2.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1583" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/BIRDY_REFINERY_29_2.jpg" alt="BIRDY_REFINERY_29_2" width="1600" height="1067" /></a> <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/BIRDY_REFINERY_29_1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1582" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/BIRDY_REFINERY_29_1.jpg" alt="BIRDY_REFINERY_29_1" width="460" height="552" /></a>For Birdy, I decided on a simple cat eye, nude lips + really didn''t touch that gal''s skin- it is flawless. Check out the full article <a href="http://www.refinery29.com/2014/05/67177/birdy-interview#slide" target="_blank"><em>here</em></a>. X', 'NEW WORK/ Birdy for REFINERY 29', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'new-work-birdy-for-refinery-29', '', '', '2015-02-04 06:50:05', '2015-02-04 06:50:05', '', 0, 'http://sarahappleby.com/blog/?p=1581', 0, 'post', '', 1),
(1588, 1, '2014-07-18 06:34:12', '2014-07-18 06:34:12', 'It is summertime in the city + with the long hot days come the challenge of keeping cool + comfortable, whilst looking effortless through it all. This makes for some fun challenges! Here is how I keep my hair looking natural + messy, [bed head if you will] with only two products...<!--more-->\r\n\r\nOribe has an amazing range of consumer friendly hair styling products. As my hair is extremely fine + poker straight, it is most difficult when it is freshly washed. Once I have towel dried my hair, I apply the <a href="http://www.oribe.com/index.php/products/view/2228/surfcomber-small-tousled-texture-mousse-small/featured:1" target="_blank">Surfcomber Tousled Texture Mousse</a>. I use a small amount + focus on my roots, blow dry it in. This gives the hair an amazing lift + almost a gritty feeling to the roots. I will follow up with the infamous <a href="http://www.oribe.com/index.php/products/view/26/dry-texturizing-spray/" target="_blank">Dry Texturizing Spray</a> + apply it to the hair shaft. I rub my hair in between my two palms quickly to activate the product + build texture.<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1590" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/MESSY_TEXTURED_MORNING_HAIR_SARAH_APPLEBY.jpg" alt="Processed with VSCOcam with f2 preset" width="2791" height="1860" /><img class="aligncenter wp-image-1592 size-full" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/MESSY_TEXTURED_MORNING_HAIR_SARAH_APPLEBY3-e1405651348420.jpg" alt="Processed with VSCOcam with f2 preset" width="1280" height="853" />Voila! Say goodbye to flat, shiny, clean hair... HAPPY SUMMER! X', 'HOW TO/ Summer''s Best Mess [=hair]', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'how-to-summers-best-mess-hair', '', '', '2015-01-27 11:26:08', '2015-01-27 11:26:08', '', 0, 'http://sarahappleby.com/blog/?p=1588', 0, 'post', '', 1),
(1597, 1, '2014-07-23 15:43:02', '2014-07-23 15:43:02', 'A few months back I had the opportunity to shoot this editorial for Seventeen Magazine with Anna Palma. Love her work so much! We shot in the Metropolitan Building in LIC, this majestic spot that makes you feel like you''re in a massive mansion, but the lookf + feel is different on every floor. It is used a lot for shoots + weddings etc. Anyway, we did some fun summer makeup on three gals...<!--more-->\r\n\r\nWe differentiated three different types of gals that will be gallivanting around this summer...\r\n\r\nCasual Glam girl has soft makeup, maybe a cute cateye or a poppy lip, but she is the one keeping it fresh + natural, using <a href="http://www.avon.ca/shop/ProductDisplay?storeId=10651&amp;urlLangId=11&amp;productId=93008&amp;urlRequestType=Base&amp;langId=11&amp;catalogId=50035#.U8_XXaj2nqs" target="_blank">Mark Blooming Pretty HIghlighting Face Powder</a>.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/SEVENTEEN_MAGAZINE_MAKEUP_SARAH_APPLEBY_ANNA_PALMA_4.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1601" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/SEVENTEEN_MAGAZINE_MAKEUP_SARAH_APPLEBY_ANNA_PALMA_4.jpg" alt="SEVENTEEN_MAGAZINE_MAKEUP_SARAH_APPLEBY_ANNA_PALMA_4" width="558" height="756" /></a>Then the Club Cutie, she is life of the party + loves a bold statement color, like the turquoise I placed on her lower lashline here. She has FUN with her makeup, + more daring then most playing with the dark blue on her lips, like the <a href="http://www.manicpanic.com/lips.html" target="_blank">Manic Panic Lethal Lipstick in Midnight Blue</a> + etc.<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1599" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/SEVENTEEN_MAGAZINE_MAKEUP_SARAH_APPLEBY_ANNA_PALMA_2.jpg" alt="SEVENTEEN_MAGAZINE_MAKEUP_SARAH_APPLEBY_ANNA_PALMA_2" width="879" height="1200" /><a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/SEVENTEEN_MAGAZINE_MAKEUP_SARAH_APPLEBY_ANNA_PALMA_5.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1602" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/SEVENTEEN_MAGAZINE_MAKEUP_SARAH_APPLEBY_ANNA_PALMA_5.jpg" alt="SEVENTEEN_MAGAZINE_MAKEUP_SARAH_APPLEBY_ANNA_PALMA_5" width="566" height="770" /></a>The World Traveler makes it all look so easy. She is bright + golden, plays with dewy skin + peachy lips. This is the low key, but kept, au natural beauty with her <a href="http://tartecosmetics.com/tarte-item-golden-days-sultry-nights-amazonian-clay-shadow-palette" target="_blank">Tarte Eyeshadow Palette</a><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1600" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/SEVENTEEN_MAGAZINE_MAKEUP_SARAH_APPLEBY_ANNA_PALMA_3.jpg" alt="SEVENTEEN_MAGAZINE_MAKEUP_SARAH_APPLEBY_ANNA_PALMA_3" width="879" height="1200" /><a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/SEVENTEEN_MAGAZINE_MAKEUP_SARAH_APPLEBY_ANNA_PALMA_6.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1603" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/SEVENTEEN_MAGAZINE_MAKEUP_SARAH_APPLEBY_ANNA_PALMA_6.jpg" alt="SEVENTEEN_MAGAZINE_MAKEUP_SARAH_APPLEBY_ANNA_PALMA_6" width="558" height="756" /></a>Which gal will you be emanating this summer? X', 'NEW WORK/ Seventeen Magazine shot by the incredible ANNA PALMA', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'new-work-seventeen-magazine-shot-by-the-incredible-anna-palma', '', '', '2015-01-27 11:27:17', '2015-01-27 11:27:17', '', 0, 'http://sarahappleby.com/blog/?p=1597', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(1605, 1, '2014-07-24 03:40:49', '2014-07-24 03:40:49', 'It is that time of year, + our feet are starving for attention. I have such joy when I get a pedicure + leave the salon feeling fresh + clean. Here are my favorite four must haves that all of us need to feel ready to bare those toes!<!--more-->\r\n\r\nI have recently been introduced to the new Clarisonic Pedi, it is a DREAM. I don''t think anyone in NYC has an excuse for rough looking nails due to the exceptionally low prices + abundance of nail salons. However, it can be difficult at times to find the hour to get your nails done... Cue <a href="http://www.clarisonic.com/shop-our-products/clarisonic-pedi-sonic-foot-transformation-887242003125.html" target="_blank">Clarisonic Pedi</a>. It''s a buffer + a moisturizer + a life changer. This finally makes the proper pedi at home achievable! + What an amazing kit, it has everything. Get to scrubbing...<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/CLARISONIC_PEDI_FOOT_CARE_SUMMER_MUSTHAVES.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1607" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/CLARISONIC_PEDI_FOOT_CARE_SUMMER_MUSTHAVES.jpg" alt="CLARISONIC_PEDI_FOOT_CARE_SUMMER_MUSTHAVES" width="2208" height="1248" /></a>Along with that goodness, you need an excellent SPF. Most recently I have been soaking my feet in <a href="http://www.clarinsusa.com/en/sun-sun-protection/410/?cm_mmc=Google-_-New%20Clarins%20Sun-_-Brand%20Sun-_-clarins%20spf&amp;gclid=Cj0KEQjwur2eBRDtvMS0gIuS-dYBEiQANBPMR3ifuKmok8JwOd2uofFBmL8gCejZh1r4MRALEhodpfMaAp2O8P8HAQ" target="_blank">Clarins SPF 15</a> Sunscreen Spray. It is a spray that is easy to apply + easy to maintain throughout your beach adventures. Nobody wants burnt feet.<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/SPF_CLARINS_SUNSCREEN_SUMMER_MUSTHAVES.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1609" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/SPF_CLARINS_SUNSCREEN_SUMMER_MUSTHAVES.jpg" alt="SPF_CLARINS_SUNSCREEN_SUMMER_MUSTHAVES" width="2208" height="1248" /></a>Then for the nail color, nothing says summer like a coral. My newest obsession is <a href="http://www.amazon.com/OPI-Nail-Polish-Spicy-NLH43/dp/B0036US0JY#" target="_blank">OPI''s Nail Laquer in Hot + Spicy.</a> The perfect amount of color + lasts for days.<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1608" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/OPI_NAIL_POLISH_SUMMER_MUSTHAVES.jpg" alt="OPI_NAIL_POLISH_SUMMER_MUSTHAVES" width="2208" height="1248" />Last but not least, every gal needs a new pair of platforms to run around town in the heat. I love <a href="http://www.zara.com/us/en/sale/woman/shoes/strappy-leather-sandal-with-track-sole-c541568p1832544.html" target="_blank">Zara </a>for up to date fun finds. These black + white platform, pinstripe pair are more than doing the trick with the perfect balance of comfort + fashion.<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/ZARA_SANDALS_FASHION_SUMMER_MUSTHAVES.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1610" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/ZARA_SANDALS_FASHION_SUMMER_MUSTHAVES.jpg" alt="ZARA_SANDALS_FASHION_SUMMER_MUSTHAVES" width="2208" height="1248" /></a>\r\n\r\nHere is hoping for a Happy Summer with really Happy Feet! X', 'HOW TO/ happy feet', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'how-to-happy-feet', '', '', '2015-01-27 11:28:06', '2015-01-27 11:28:06', '', 0, 'http://sarahappleby.com/blog/?p=1605', 0, 'post', '', 0),
