g/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/ICING_CAMPAIGN_KEHOE_2014_5.jpg" alt="ICING_CAMPAIGN_KEHOE_2014_5" width="1000" height="1500" /></a> <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/ICING_CAMPAIGN_KEHOE_2014_6.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1624" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/ICING_CAMPAIGN_KEHOE_2014_6.jpg" alt="ICING_CAMPAIGN_KEHOE_2014_6" width="1000" height="1500" /></a> <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/ICING_CAMPAIGN_KEHOE_2014_7.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1625" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/ICING_CAMPAIGN_KEHOE_2014_7.jpg" alt="ICING_CAMPAIGN_KEHOE_2014_7" width="1000" height="1500" /></a> <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/ICING_CAMPAIGN_KEHOE_2014_8.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1626" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/ICING_CAMPAIGN_KEHOE_2014_8.jpg" alt="ICING_CAMPAIGN_KEHOE_2014_8" width="1000" height="1500" /></a> <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/ICING_CAMPAIGN_KEHOE_2014_9.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1627" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/ICING_CAMPAIGN_KEHOE_2014_9.jpg" alt="ICING_CAMPAIGN_KEHOE_2014_9" width="1000" height="1500" /></a>I used a lot of metallics on the eye, matte stains on the lip + Icing loves a poppy cheek! Always fun to play with girlie makeup. You can see the rest of the campaign images on the Icing site... X', 'NEW WORK/ Icing Campaign shoot', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'new-work-icing-campaign-shoot', '', '', '2015-01-27 11:28:39', '2015-01-27 11:28:39', '', 0, 'http://sarahappleby.com/blog/?p=1618', 0, 'post', '', 1);
