(1631, 1, '2014-08-19 11:33:59', '2014-08-19 11:33:59', 'A little while back I worked on this editorial for Farfetch, featuring model + tech guru, Lyndsey Scott. Photos by Thomas Giddings, Styling by Sarah Cobb + Hair + Makeup by moi...<!--more-->\r\n\r\nLyndsey has beautiful skin which I wanted to feature so we kept everything really simple + clean. The two main products to get the look: Armani Beauty''s <a href="http://www.giorgioarmanibeauty-usa.com/on/demandware.store/Sites-armani_us-Site/default/Product-Show?pid=A247&amp;bookmark=599669" target="_blank">Face Fabric</a> + then highlighted her cheekbones, nose, + top lip with Benefit''s <a href="http://www.benefitcosmetics.com/product/view/high-beam" target="_blank">High Beam</a> creating a luminous + dewy feel which complemented the clothing beautifully.<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/140711_Farfetch_B_080.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1634" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/140711_Farfetch_B_080.jpg" alt="140711_Farfetch_B_080" width="2519" height="1440" /></a><a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/140711_Farfetch_A_066_bw.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1633" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/140711_Farfetch_A_066_bw.jpg" alt="140711_Farfetch_A_066_bw" width="2160" height="1440" /></a>\r\n\r\nCheck out <a href="http://www.farfetch.com/editorial/great-scott.aspx" target="_blank">Farfetch</a> to see the whole interview, Lyndsey is a little smartie, + beautiful woman in + out! X', 'NEW WORK/ Farfetch Editorial with Lyndsey Scott', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'new-work-farfetch-editorial-with-lyndsey-scott', '', '', '2015-01-27 11:22:10', '2015-01-27 11:22:10', '', 0, 'http://sarahappleby.com/blog/?p=1631', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(1638, 1, '2014-09-03 17:41:56', '2014-09-03 17:41:56', '&nbsp;\r\n\r\nI have recently become obsessed with two makeup products, I will no longer live without. You need both of these products for this luminous skin dreamteam! Get into it...<!--more-->\r\n\r\n<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1640" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/ARMANI_LUMINOUS_SKIN_MAKEUP_BLOG_POST1.jpg" alt="ARMANI_LUMINOUS_SKIN_MAKEUP_BLOG_POST1" width="1988" height="1152" />The new musthaves: [Armani Beauty killing it with the products for skin.]\r\n\r\nThe <a href="http://www.giorgioarmanibeauty-usa.com/on/demandware.store/Sites-armani_us-Site/default/Product-Show?pid=A044&amp;bookmark=343105" target="_blank">Fluid Sheer</a> comes in twelve shades + all are glorious. My favorte shades, for lighter skin use shade #2, for medium skin [moi!] use shade #10 + for darker skin tones, use #11.Â  After moisturizing clean skin I put a pump of the Fluid Sheer in my fingers + rub into the highlights of my face [think almost everywhere except around the eyes, nose + mouth].\r\n\r\nThen follow with <a href="http://www.giorgioarmanibeauty-usa.com/face-fabric-foundation-spf-12/A247,default,pd.html?dwvar_A247_color=5%20-%20dark%20beige&amp;start=1&amp;cgid=foundation&amp;cm_vc=Search&amp;q=face%20fabric" target="_blank">Face Fabric</a>. This is categorized as a longwear, full coverage foundation- it is not! It glides on so smoothly with light to medium coverage. + Layered on top of the Fluid Sheer gives it a beautiful translucent quality on the skin. Make sure you blend! As there are only five shades, be sure to try it out before you buy to ensure you have the right color. These are also BEAUTIFUL for darker skin tones.\r\n\r\nThere you go! My secret to some dewy, healthy skin... X', 'MAKEUP MUST HAVES: for the most luminous skin', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'makeup-must-haves-for-the-most-luminous-skin', '', '', '2015-01-27 11:22:42', '2015-01-27 11:22:42', '', 0, 'http://sarahappleby.com/blog/?p=1638', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(1643, 1, '2014-09-19 16:31:52', '2014-09-19 16:31:52', '<iframe style="border: none;" src="http://abcnews.go.com/video/embed?id=25569286" width="640" height="360" scrolling="no"></iframe>\r\n<a href="http://abcnews.go.com/video">More ABC news videos</a> | <a href="http://abcnews.go.com/international">Latest world news</a>\r\n\r\nWednesday [VERY early morning] I headed up to the Good Morning America studios to paint the faces of UK electronic group, Clean Bandit. They all have a structured yet effortless style... <!--more-->\r\n\r\nFor the gals, it was all about dewy skin, fresh + natural with feathery lashes. I used Armani Beauty Fluid Master Primer as a base + then buffed the Fluid Sheers [5+8] over cheeks + t zone as a base. That gives the skin a gorgeous glow. For the brows I used Armani Brow Defining Pencils.\r\n\r\nThe girls [+ guys!] were a pleasure to work with! Can''t wait to see what happens for them next. X', 'NEW WORK: Clean Bandit performs on Good Morning America!', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'new-work-clean-bandit-performs-on-good-morning-america', '', '', '2015-01-27 11:16:45', '2015-01-27 11:16:45', '', 0, 'http://sarahappleby.com/blog/?p=1643', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(1652, 1, '2014-10-09 16:12:24', '2014-10-09 16:12:24', '<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_ModTest_SARAH_KEHOE_HEIDI_VERSTER_ISAAC_WEBER_3.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1657" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_ModTest_SARAH_KEHOE_HEIDI_VERSTER_ISAAC_WEBER_3.jpg" alt="2014_ModTest_SARAH_KEHOE_HEIDI_VERSTER_ISAAC_WEBER_3" width="3840" height="5760" /></a>A new cute editorial story; Heidi Verster + Isaac Weber are two faves of mine! We were telling the story of two mod lovebirds running around Brooklyn... It was a fun day with a lovely crew.<!--more-->\r\n\r\nWe were all inspired by a 60''s feel, I kept Heidi''s skin really bright using <a href="http://www.chanel.com/en_US/fragrance-beauty/Makeup-Base-LE-BLANC-DE-CHANEL-138459/sku/138460" target="_blank">Le Blanc De Chanel.</a> It is a multi use luminating cream, I often use after moisturizing, before foundation. Of course, Brigitte Bardot was famous for her sexy winged liner, which I recreated here using <a href="http://www.bobbibrowncosmetics.com/product/2328/7785/Makeup/Eyes/Eyeliner/Long-Wear-Gel-Eyeliner/index.tmpl#i.p9htwr26adbv10" target="_blank">Bobbi Brown''s Long-Wear Gel Eyeliner in Black Ink.</a> I softened the top of the liner with my fingers slightly, to make for a more modern look.<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_ModTest_SARAH_KEHOE_HEIDI_VERSTER_ISAAC_WEBER_1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1656" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_ModTest_SARAH_KEHOE_HEIDI_VERSTER_ISAAC_WEBER_1.jpg" alt="2014_ModTest_SARAH_KEHOE_HEIDI_VERSTER_ISAAC_WEBER_1" width="1938" height="1500" /></a> <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_ModTest_SARAH_KEHOE_HEIDI_VERSTER_ISAAC_WEBER_6.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1660" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_ModTest_SARAH_KEHOE_HEIDI_VERSTER_ISAAC_WEBER_6.jpg" alt="2014_ModTest_SARAH_KEHOE_HEIDI_VERSTER_ISAAC_WEBER_6" width="2250" height="1500" /></a> <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_ModTest_SARAH_KEHOE_HEIDI_VERSTER_ISAAC_WEBER_5.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1659" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_ModTest_SARAH_KEHOE_HEIDI_VERSTER_ISAAC_WEBER_5.jpg" alt="2014_ModTest_SARAH_KEHOE_HEIDI_VERSTER_ISAAC_WEBER_5" width="1000" height="1500" /></a> <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_ModTest_SARAH_KEHOE_HEIDI_VERSTER_ISAAC_WEBER_4.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1658" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_ModTest_SARAH_KEHOE_HEIDI_VERSTER_ISAAC_WEBER_4.jpg" alt="2014_ModTest_SARAH_KEHOE_HEIDI_VERSTER_ISAAC_WEBER_4" width="1000" height="1500" /></a> <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_ModTest_SARAH_KEHOE_H-copy.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1655" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_ModTest_SARAH_KEHOE_H-copy.jpg" alt="2014_ModTest_SARAH_KEHOE_H copy" width="1000" height="1500" /></a> <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_042_ModTest_Shot_03_097.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1654" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_042_ModTest_Shot_03_097.jpg" alt="2014_042_ModTest_Shot_03_097" width="2051" height="1500" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_ModTest_SARAH_KEHOE_HEIDI_VERSTER_ISAAC_WEBER_6.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1660" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_ModTest_SARAH_KEHOE_HEIDI_VERSTER_ISAAC_WEBER_6.jpg" alt="2014_ModTest_SARAH_KEHOE_HEIDI_VERSTER_ISAAC_WEBER_6" width="2250" height="1500" /></a>Sarah Kehoe photographed the story, Alexis Zipp styled + Hair was done by David Cruz.', 'NEW 