(1664, 1, '2014-10-22 11:00:21', '2014-10-22 11:00:21', 'The last few weeks I have been working with French designer, Alix Petit, on her presentation for Heimstone''s latest collection: Imperial Summer 2015. Last nite, it all came to life at French establishment, Laduree, in Soho. Only fitting that one of my favorite French skincare brand, <a href="http://us.caudalie.com/" target="_blank">Caudalie</a> came on board to sponsor the event. I had an amazing team of girls that helped me bring Alix''s Safari influence + new collection to life with beautifully contoured + sunkissed skin...Â <!--more-->\r\n\r\n<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_HEIMSTONE_SUMMER_PRESENTATION_MAKEUP_BTS_03.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1667" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_HEIMSTONE_SUMMER_PRESENTATION_MAKEUP_BTS_03.jpg" alt="2014_HEIMSTONE_SUMMER_PRESENTATION_MAKEUP_BTS_03" width="2880" height="1789" /></a>When talking about a Safari, I immediately think of sun kissed + glowy skin. To begin prepping the girls, I used a very generous amount of the <a href="http://us.caudalie.com/organic-grape-water.html" target="_blank">Caudalie Grape Water spray</a> which soothes + moisturizes the skin, following with <a href="http://us.caudalie.com/shop-products/concern-1/dark-spot-correction/radiance-serum-complexion-correcting.html" target="_blank">Radiance Serum</a> all over the face. Then onto <a href="http://uk.caudalie.com/broad-spectrum-sfp20-anti-wrinkle-protect-fluid.html" target="_blank">Broad Spectrum SPF20 Anti-Wrinkle Protect Fluid</a>. Any cream with SPF in it will give the skin a slight glow due to the zinc. I love this new product, it has grape polyphenols in it, known to fight free radicals [free radicals are found to be responsible for 80% of wrinkles].<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1682" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_HEIMSTONE_SUMMER_PRESENTATION_MAKEUP_BTS_19.jpg" alt="Processed with VSCOcam with f2 preset" width="3264" height="2176" />\r\n\r\nIt was all about body too. <a href="http://us.caudalie.com/vine-body-butter-1.html" target="_blank">Caudalie''s Vine Body Butter</a> nourishes + repairs the skin, then to finish legs, arms + dÃ©colletage I sprayed the <a href="http://us.caudalie.com/divine-oil.html" target="_blank">Divine Oil</a> on the girls.Â <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_HEIMSTONE_SUMMER_PRESENTATION_MAKEUP_BTS_18.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-1681 size-full" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_HEIMSTONE_SUMMER_PRESENTATION_MAKEUP_BTS_18-e1414077616566.jpg" alt="Processed with VSCOcam with f2 preset" width="2448" height="1958" /></a>For makeup I did an obvious warm brown creamy contour on the eyes, sharp brows with a beautiful brow highlight. My favorite trick for highlighting skin without sparkles or shimmer is to use <a href="http://us.caudalie.com/premier-cru-the-eye-cream-1.html" target="_blank">Caudalie''s Premier Cru, The Eye Cream</a>. Using fingers to pat it below brow + through the c-section on the top of the cheekbones.Â  All the girls lips were a nude berry. To finish the look, I sprayed the famous <a href="http://us.caudalie.com/beauty-elixir-full-size.html" target="_blank">Beauty Elixir</a> to set the makeup + finish the skin with a radiant glow.<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_HEIMSTONE_SUMMER_PRESENTATION_MAKEUP_BTS_17.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1680" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_HEIMSTONE_SUMMER_PRESENTATION_MAKEUP_BTS_17.jpg" alt="2014_HEIMSTONE_SUMMER_PRESENTATION_MAKEUP_BTS_17" width="3264" height="2176" /></a>Â Alix + her twin sister Caroline, along with the beauties of Heimstone outside of Laduree before the presentation started. Â <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_HEIMSTONE_SUMMER_PRESENTATION_MAKEUP_BTS_16.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1679" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_HEIMSTONE_SUMMER_PRESENTATION_MAKEUP_BTS_16.jpg" alt="2014_HEIMSTONE_SUMMER_PRESENTATION_MAKEUP_BTS_16" width="2823" height="1882" /></a><a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_HEIMSTONE_SUMMER_PRESENTATION_MAKEUP_BTS_02.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1666" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_HEIMSTONE_SUMMER_PRESENTATION_MAKEUP_BTS_02.jpg" alt="2014_HEIMSTONE_SUMMER_PRESENTATION_MAKEUP_BTS_02" width="3315" height="2101" /></a>Â Â  <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_HEIMSTONE_SUMMER_PRESENTATION_MAKEUP_BTS_21.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1684" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_HEIMSTONE_SUMMER_PRESENTATION_MAKEUP_BTS_21.jpg" alt="2014_HEIMSTONE_SUMMER_PRESENTATION_MAKEUP_BTS_21" width="2432" height="1621" /></a>Â  <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_HEIMSTONE_SUMMER_PRESENTATION_MAKEUP_BTS_06.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1670" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_HEIMSTONE_SUMMER_PRESENTATION_MAKEUP_BTS_06.jpg" alt="2014_HEIMSTONE_SUMMER_PRESENTATION_MAKEUP_BTS_06" width="3804" height="3336" /></a> <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_HEIMSTONE_SUMMER_PRESENTATION_MAKEUP_BTS_07.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1671" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_HEIMSTONE_SUMMER_PRESENTATION_MAKEUP_BTS_07.jpg" alt="2014_HEIMSTONE_SUMMER_PRESENTATION_MAKEUP_BTS_07" width="4362" height="3245" /></a> Backstage touch ups before they went into the Jungle!<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_HEIMSTONE_SUMMER_PRESENTATION_MAKEUP_BTS_08.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1672" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_HEIMSTONE_SUMMER_PRESENTATION_MAKEUP_BTS_08.jpg" alt="2014_HEIMSTONE_SUMMER_PRESENTATION_MAKEUP_BTS_08" width="5052" height="3029" /></a> <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_HEIMSTONE_SUMMER_PRESENTATION_MAKEUP_BTS_09.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1673" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_HEIMSTONE_SUMMER_PRESENTATION_MAKEUP_BTS_09.jpg" alt="2014_HEIMSTONE_SUMMER_PRESENTATION_MAKEUP_BTS_09" width="3456" height="4858" /></a> <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_HEIMSTONE_SUMMER_PRESENTATION_MAKEUP_BTS_10.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1674" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_HEIMSTONE_SUMMER_PRESENTATION_MAKEUP_BTS_10.jpg" alt="2014_HEIMSTONE_SUMMER_PRESENTATION_MAKEUP_BTS_10" width="3456" height="3972" /></a> <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_HEIMSTONE_SUMMER_PRESENTATION_MAKEUP_BTS_11.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1675" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_HEIMSTONE_SUMMER_PRESENTATION_MAKEUP_BTS_11.jpg" alt="2014_HEIMSTONE_SUMMER_PRESENTATION_MAKEUP_BTS_11" width="4264" height="2794" /></a> Kelsey Morgan, on left, headed up the hair team, beautiful.<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_HEIMSTONE_SUMMER_PRESENTATION_MAKEUP_BTS_12.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1676" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_HEIMSTONE_SUMMER_PRESENTATION_MAKEUP_BTS_12.jpg" alt="2014_HEIMSTONE_SUMMER_PRESENTATION_MAKEUP_BTS_12" width="5184" height="3456" /></a>Â  <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_HEIMSTONE_SUMMER_PRESENTATION_MAKEUP_BTS_14.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1678" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_HEIMSTONE_SUMMER_PRESENTATION_MAKEUP_BTS_14.jpg" alt="2014_HEIMSTONE_SUMMER_PRESENTATION_MAKEUP_BTS_14" width="5184" height="3456" /></a><a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_HEIMSTONE_SUMMER_PRESENTATION_MAKEUP_BTS_20.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1683" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_HEIMSTONE_SUMMER_PRESENTATION_MAKEUP_BTS_20.jpg" alt="Processed with VSCOcam with f2 preset" width="2970" height="1980" /></a>Such a fun day + nite celebrating the launch. Congratulations Heimstone! It was such a beautiful nite at Laduree.\r\n\r\n[photos by myself + Nick Demaino].', 'NEW WORK: Key Makeup for Heimstone Summer 2015 presentation', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'new-work-key-makeup-for-heimstone-summer-2015-presentation', '', '', '2015-01-27 11:17:39', '2015-01-27 11:17:39', '', 0, 'http://sarahappleby.com/blog/?p=1664', 0, 'post', '', 3),
(1692, 1, '2014-10-27 16:37:53', '2014-10-27 16:37:53', 'Last week, I had the pleasure of working with 17 year old, music sensation Jacquie Lee. We hopped around New York so she could perform her single ''Broken Ones'' off of her new EP that was just released! Along with being one of the sweetest gals around, her voice is astounding- like nothing you have heard before. + On top of all of that goodness, she is beautiful making it for easy work days...<!--more-->\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nFor her performance on The Today Show, we did creamy navy eyes using <a href="http://www.narscosmetics.com/USA/eyeshadow" target="_blank">Nars Soft Touch Shadow Pencil in Navy Rite</a>, + used <a href="http://www.oribe.com/index.php/products/view/26/dry-texturizing-spray/" target="_blank">Oribe Dry Texturizing Spray</a> throughout the body of her hair for that tousled look.\r\n\r\n<object id="msnbc52bccd" width="420" height="245" classid="clsid:D27CDB6E-AE6D-11cf-96B8-444553540000" codebase="http://download.macromedia.com/pub/shockwave/cabs/flash/swflash.cab#version=10,0,0,0"><param name="movie" value="http://www.nbcnews.com/id/32545640" /><param name="FlashVars" value="launch=56271684&amp;width=420&amp;height=245" /><param name="allowScriptAccess" value="always" /><param name="allowFullScreen" value="true" /><param name="wmode" value="transparent" /><embed name="msnbc52bccd" src="http://www.nbcnews.com/id/32545640" width="420" height="245" flashvars="launch=56271684&amp;width=420&amp;height=245" allowscriptaccess="always" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen" wmode="transparent" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" pluginspage="http://www.adobe.com/shockwave/download/download.cgi?P1_Prod_Version=ShockwaveFlash" /></object>\r\n\r\nOn VH1 we went for softer eyes,Â <a href="http://www.narscosmetics.com/USA/eyeshadow" target="_blank">NARS Shimmer Eyeshadow in Galapagos</a> + smoother hair using <a href="http://www.oribe.com/index.php/products/view/1784/supershine-light-moisturizing-cream/" target="_blank">Oribe Super Shine Light Moisturizing Cream</a> for a more polished look.\r\n\r\n<iframe src="http://media.mtvnservices.com/embed/mgid:uma:video:vh1.com:1090812/cp~vid%3D1090812%26uri%3Dmgid%3Auma%3Avideo%3Avh1.com%3A1090812" width="512" height="288" frameborder="0"></iframe>\r\nA fun few days with Jacquie + crew. The lovely James Demolet styling, I say A-team. Here are a few [iPhone] snaps from the days. I cannot wait to see where this beauty goes...<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/SARAH_APPLEBY_JACQUIE_LEE_3.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-1697 size-full" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/SARAH_APPLEBY_JACQUIE_LEE_3-e1414427455934.jpg" alt="SARAH_APPLEBY_JACQUIE_LEE_3" width="1062" height="708" /></a> <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/SARAH_APPLEBY_JACQUIE_LEE.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-1698 size-full" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/SARAH_APPLEBY_JACQUIE_LEE-e1414427482677.jpg" alt="Processed with VSCOcam with f2 preset" width="896" height="896" /></a>', 'NEW WORK: Hair + Makeup for Jacquie Lee''s press days ', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'new-work-hair-makeup-for-jacquie-lees-press-days', '', '', '2015-01-27 11:06:12', '2015-01-27 11:06:12', '', 0, 'http://sarahappleby.com/blog/?p=1692', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(1705, 1, '2014-11-06 16:33:38', '2014-11-06 16:33:38', 'I have gone on the hunt lately to find some new seasonal must haves. If you keep up with this blog, you know what a fan I am of changing your look with the season. I have put together a few new favorites, that are seasonally appropriate as the colors + temperatures are changing...<!--more-->I love a good bronzer set. But! Away with the shimmery bronzers, Miami tan look. I love this new Flushed palette in Strip by Urban Decay. It has a beautiful bronzer which I use for contour, a highlighter I place above my cheekbones + browbones + a pretty, cool toned, pink blush for a touch on the apples of my cheek.<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/2014_BLOG_FALL_FAVORITES_ARMANI_MAC_ANASTASIA_NAKED_5.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1710" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/2014_BLOG_FALL_FAVORITES_ARMANI_MAC_ANASTASIA_NAKED_5.jpg" alt="2014_BLOG_FALL_FAVORITES_ARMANI_MAC_ANASTASIA_NAKED_5" width="3460" height="1995" /></a> After a summer of brushed through soft brows, I am stepping up the structure with Anastasia Beverly Hills Dipbrow Pomade. Using an angle liner brush I take a small amount [a little goes a long way!] + making tiny brush strokes in an upwards motion to create a natural effect. Then wisping around the top edges of brown to create arch. I love the tone of Taupe, so beautiful, a great ashy option for blondes/dirty blondes.<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1711" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/2014_BLOG_FALL_FAVORITES_ARMANI_MAC_ANASTASIA_NAKED_6.jpg" alt="2014_BLOG_FALL_FAVORITES_ARMANI_MAC_ANASTASIA_NAKED_6" width="3049" height="1514" />The quickest way to get a polished look quickly is to pop a lip. Here are my new favorite fall must have lipsticks. From left to right:\r\n\r\nMAC Cosmetics Matte in <a href="http://www.maccosmetics.com/product/shaded/168/310/Lipstick/index.tmpl" target="_blank">So Chaud</a> [what i am wearing in the photo above]\r\n\r\nArmani <a href="http://www.giorgioarmanibeauty-usa.com/on/demandware.store/Sites-armani_us-Site/default/Product-Show?pid=A439&amp;bookmark=363243" target="_blank">Rouge Ecstasy in 404</a>\r\n\r\nMAC Cosmetics <a href="http://www.maccosmetics.com/product/shaded/13432/310/New-Collections/The-Matte-Lip/Lips/Lipstick/index.tmpl" target="_blank">Flat Out Fabulous</a>\r\n\r\nA poppy, orangy red, classic red + a bright berry.<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/2014_BLOG_FALL_FAVORITES_ARMANI_MAC_ANASTASIA_NAKED_4.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1709" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/2014_BLOG_FALL_FAVORITES_ARMANI_MAC_ANASTASIA_NAKED_4.jpg" alt="2014_BLOG_FALL_FAVORITES_ARMANI_MAC_ANASTASIA_NAKED_4" width="3420" height="2166" /></a>Here is to layers + hot drinks + crisp neighborhood strolls.. X', 'USE: A Few Favorites for Fall', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'use-a-few-favorites-for-fall', '', '', '2015-01-27 11:04:00', '2015-01-27 11:04:00', '', 0, 'http://sarahappleby.com/blog/?p=1705', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(1716, 1, '2014-12-01 01:41:57', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'A new Knits story shot by Sarah Kehoe + styled by one of my nearest + dearest, Morgan Gibbons. It is a cozy dreamy story with knits for days in a big old haunted house in Staten Island...\n\n&nbsp;\n\nLove the tones + palette Morgan pulled. I decided to throw in a little 90''s vibe with rust, brown, berry tones on the lips, yet keeping the face all very monochromatic. X', 'NEW WORK: Knits Editorial with Sarah Kehoe', '', 'draft', 'open', 'open', '', '', '', '', '2014-12-01 01:41:57', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', 0, 'http://sarahappleby.com/blog/?p=1716', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(1717, 1, '2013-04-12 23:37:36', '2013-04-12 23:37:36', '&nbsp;\r\n\r\nToday, I worked with one of my favorite clients, Saks 5th Ave, on an upcoming editorial for D+G. Gorgeous Nika modeling, made it easy for beauty. A few sneak peek shots from the day...<!--more-->\r\n\r\nFresh face; cleansed, moisturized.<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/nika.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-469" alt="nika" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/nika.jpg" width="2176" height="3264" /></a>\r\n\r\nThe look: a neutral brown contour on the eyes, light fill of the brows, lots of mascara + a poppy creamy pink lip.<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/nika11.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-478" alt="nika1" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/nika11.jpg" width="1854" height="2780" /></a>Frocks for days...<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/nika3.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-470" alt="nika3" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/nika3.jpg" width="2176" height="3264" /></a><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-479" alt="nika4" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/nika42.jpg" width="2176" height="3264" />Then a more sultry look, I am such a fan of the deep purple shade on the lip.<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/nika51.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-480" alt="nika5" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/nika51.jpg" width="2176" height="3264" /></a>Final Images to come!', 'Behind the Scenes/ Saks 5th Avenue', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'work-journal-saks-5th-avenue', '', '', '2015-01-28 06:30:37', '2015-01-28 06:30:37', '', 0, 'http://sarahappleby.com/blog/?p=467', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(1718, 1, '2013-04-16 11:00:25', '2013-04-16 11:00:25', 'If I had a penny for every time someone asked me what my beauty ''rules'' are... I don''t really have rules. With makeup, hair, or fashion. I love the creative freedom of others + appreciate how they interpret beauty. However, there has been one consistent exception. Love your skin well. Which to me, means [+ not limited to] washing your face every evening + putting it to bed. Nearly half of your life is spent sleeping + the thought of it being caked with makeup, layered with dirty dusty air, + more, makes it not ok to not get this bedtime routine down!<!--more-->\r\n\r\nI love to switch up my products + try new skincare routines, but as of late, here is the go to...<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/photo-2-1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-496" alt="photo 2-1" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/photo-2-1.jpg" width="3264" height="2174" /></a>â€¢Makeup or no makeup day, I start with <a href="http://www.dermalogica.com/precleanse/1,default,pd.html" target="_blank">Dermalogica''s Precleanse</a>, it''s a gentle [plant based!] oil that lifts makeup, unwanted environmental pollutants, skincare products + more.\r\n\r\nâ€¢I apply <a href="http://www.sephora.com/deep-cleansing-exfoliator-P374574" target="_blank">Caudalie Deep Cleansing Exfoliator</a> with my hands, all over my damp skin + 3-4 times a week I use it with the <a href="http://www.clarisonic.com/for_professionals/clarisonic_pro_cleansing/technology/" target="_blank">Clarisonic Pro</a> for the suggested three minutes. It feel so good to get all that extra grit sluffed off my skin. The Clarisonic is great because it is gentle, yet leaves your skin feeling deeply cleansed + exfoliated as if you''ve just had the best facial. (Post a VinoSource Facial at the Caudalie Spa in the plaza, I immediately purchased the Clarisonic).\r\n\r\nâ€¢Moisturize! I use my ring finger to dab on <a href="http://www.sephora.com/ultimate-lift-eye-gel-P42344?om_mmc=Googlepla,_requestid=42976,cm_mmc=us_search-_-GG-_-pla-_-,ci_src=17588969,ci_sku=966200" target="_blank">Ole Henriksen Ultimate Eye Lift Gel</a> around my eyes + then generously apply the <a href="http://www.sephora.com/wild-rose-vitamin-c-advanced-brightening-sleeping-facial-P306883" target="_blank">Korres Wild Rose + Vitamin C Brightening Sleeping Facial</a> all over the face + neck. It is extremely hydrating + you wake up feeling completely rejuvenated\r\n\r\nâ€¢ Finishing off with a little <a href="http://us.amorepacific.com/en/product/MOISTURE_BOUND_LIP_TREATMENT" target="_blank">Amore Pacific Moisture Bound Lip Treatment</a>, perhaps my favorite lip treatment of all time- smooth texture leaving your lips supple.\r\n\r\nâ€¢I always sleep with water next to my bed in the case I need to hydrate throughout the nite! I blow my <a href="http://www.candleluxury.com/calvin-klein-delicate-blossoms-candle.html?utm_source=GoogleProducts&amp;utm_medium=shopping%2Bengine&amp;utm_term=Calvin+Klein+Delicate+Blossoms+Candle&amp;utm_campaign=GoogleProducts&amp;gclid=CNC94J-bzrYCFQef4AodHlkAXw" target="_blank">Calvin Klein candle in Delicate Blossoms</a> out + turn the lights off.\r\n\r\nSleep well + sweet dreams! S.', 'Good Night Skin', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'good-night-skin', '', '', '2015-01-28 06:31:22', '2015-01-28 06:31:22', '', 0, 'http://sarahappleby.com/blog/?p=489', 0, 'post', '', 3),
(1719, 1, '2013-04-17 10:00:14', '2013-04-17 10:00:14', '&nbsp;\r\n\r\nI am loving the new Spring/Summer 2013 campaigns out right now [most of them- here are the standouts]... All makeup is clean + pretty + the hair is natural, textured + choppy.\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\n<strong></strong><em>Salvatore Ferragamo/</em> love the color in the hair- ombre IS still happening + when done right, gorgeous <em>Prada/</em> pretty natural berry tint on the lip  <em>Balmain/</em> center part + texture in the hair is so good, dreaming of that leather jacket! <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/photo-52.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-494" alt="photo 5" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/photo-52.jpg" width="1823" height="1367" /></a>\r\n\r\nONDRIA + <em>CHANEL</em>! To date, one of my favorite models I have worked with. I love that not only did Karl choose her for this campaign, but it caused quite the stir due to the fact that she is still so young. I think it''s a perfect fit. This story is so good. Lips + Skin!<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/photo-23.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-492" alt="photo 2" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/photo-23.jpg" width="1868" height="1402" /></a>\r\n\r\n<em>Marc Jacobs/</em> Still strong with the bleach blonde + touch a root showing through <em>Fendi/</em> I am into the glossy + slick hair, minimal makeup <em>Louis Vuitton/</em> 60''s vibe + beehive, vibrant color + bold patterns<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/photo-13.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-491" alt="photo 1" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/photo-13.jpg" width="1935" height="1451" /></a>\r\n\r\n<em>Giorgio Armani/</em> Obsessed with the short slick hair, inspiring my personal styling <em>Chloe/</em> Again, texture in the hair + the contoured eye is magic, very 70''s feeling here<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-490" alt="photo 3" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/photo-32.jpg" width="1956" height="1467" /><em>Isabel Marant/</em> Daria! Natural + flawless <em>Celine/</em> Daria! Aside from the classic no makeup makeup, I love this whole collection. Phoebe, you can do no wrong. <em>Balenciaga/</em> Any woman who needs some short hair inspiration, obsess. The short choppy bob is back.\r\n\r\nAll so good. This season has made the muted hair + makeup so desirable. I love these campaigns, all tying mood + beauty + pieces together cohesively. Very inspiring.', 'S/S13: Campaign Inspiration', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'ss13-campaign-inspiration', '', '', '2015-01-28 06:30:08', '2015-01-28 06:30:08', '', 0, 'http://sarahappleby.com/blog/?p=506', 0, 'post', '', 1),
(1720, 1, '2014-12-01 17:53:30', '2014-12-01 17:53:30', '<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/2014_POST_FAVE_MASCARA_21.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1723" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/2014_POST_FAVE_MASCARA_21.jpg" alt="2014_POST_FAVE_MASCARA_2" width="1271" height="752" /></a>One of the most frequently asked questions I get:Â  what is my favorite mascara. It seems women love to obsess over the lashes + are rarely satisfied! We are now in the season of gift sets + this is one you cannot miss out on! You all need to skip on over to Sephora to pick up their <a href="http://www.sephora.com/lashstash-P388552?skuId=1647189&amp;om_mmc=ppc-GG&amp;mkwid=lUoad1cI&amp;pcrid=49113160719&amp;pdv=c&amp;site=us_search&amp;country_switch=us&amp;lang=en&amp;gclid=CN7Z6M-SpcICFcFr7AodUhEAdA" target="_blank">LASH STASH</a> gift set. It is packed full of the very best...<!--more-->\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nYou''ll get to try TEN of the top mascaras [one full size] for only $45. I had to stock up on a few sets. Mascara tends to dry out with the first 3-4 months. Truth be told this is when I love it the most! I love a good chunky, textured lash. But These little trial tubes are the perfect size, when you''re feeling the texture changes too much, start onto the next.\r\n\r\nThe mascara you get:\r\n\r\nâ€¢ Benefit Cosmetics They''re Real Mascara In Jet Black\r\nâ€¢ Buxom Lash Mascara In Blackest Black\r\nâ€¢ Clinique Dual Ended High Impact Mascara And Lash Primer\r\nâ€¢ Josie Maran Argan Black Oil Mascara\r\nâ€¢ Kat Von D Immortal Lash 24HR Mascara\r\nâ€¢ LancÃ´me Paris HypnÃ´se Drama Mascara\r\nâ€¢ Sephora Collection Outrageous Curl Dramatic Volume And Curl Mascara\r\nâ€¢ Smashbox Full Exposure Mascara In Jet Black\r\nâ€¢ Urban Decay Perversion Mascara\r\nâ€¢ YSL Mascara Volume Effect Faux Baby Doll\r\n\r\nSo far my front runners are: Benefit, LancÃ´me, Urban Decay... What are you favorites? X\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'USE: Find your favorite mascara!', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'use-find-your-favorite-mascara', '', '', '2015-01-27 11:02:20', '2015-01-27 11:02:20', '', 0, 'http://sarahappleby.com/blog/?p=1718', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(1725, 1, '2014-12-09 15:35:51', '2014-12-09 15:35:51', 'Last week I had the opportunity to shoot an editorial story with Geoff Barrenger + model Anastasiya B<span data-reactid=".a.0.1.0.0.0.0.1.0.1.0.$868262299785805846:0.1.2:0">urachevskaya</span>. It was a chilly day up on the Hudson, stylist Melissa Infante played with muted palettes + cozy textures. I did both hair + makeup, keeping it effortless + natural with the hair + playing with contours on the skin...<!--more-->\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nFor makeup, I used all natural tones. Anastasiya already has beautiful strong brows but I shaped + refined them with the Anastasia Beverly Hills <a href="http://anastasiabeverlyhills.com/dipbrow-pomade-waterproof-color-brow-sculp.html" target="_blank">Dipbrow Pomade in Light Brown</a>. I used Makeup For Ever''s <a href="http://www.makeupforever.com/int/en-int/make-up/face/powder/sculpting-kit?sku=6131" target="_blank">Contour Kit</a> in Gold on her skin + used MAC Cosmetic''s <a href="http://www.maccosmetics.com/product/shaded/156/316/Products/Face/Cheek/Cream-Colour-Base/index.tmpl" target="_blank">Cream Colour Base in Mid Tone Sepia</a> on the lids + around the eye, followed with <a href="http://www.maccosmetics.com/product/shaded/2146/363/Bestsellers/Eye-Shadow/index.tmpl" target="_blank">Espresso eyeshadow</a> for intensity over the cream.<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/2014_ANASTASIYA_GEOFF_BARRENGER_SARAH_APPLEBY_ARMANI_BEAUTY_05.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1731" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/2014_ANASTASIYA_GEOFF_BARRENGER_SARAH_APPLEBY_ARMANI_BEAUTY_05.jpg" alt="2014_ANASTASIYA_GEOFF_BARRENGER_SARAH_APPLEBY_ARMANI_BEAUTY_05" width="2640" height="3360" /></a> <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/2014_ANASTASIYA_GEOFF_BARRENGER_SARAH_APPLEBY_ARMANI_BEAUTY_04.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1730" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/20