(1852, 1, '2015-01-27 10:19:10', '2015-01-27 10:19:10', '<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/hairNYFWss14.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1046" alt="hairNYFWss14" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/hairNYFWss14.jpg" width="3264" height="1868" /></a>This NYFW, we saw structure + texture over + over again, I am not complaining! Some clean + others a beautiful mess. Here are my favorites from the week...<!--more-->\r\n\r\nPaul Hanlon for 3.1 PHILLIP LIM:Â  <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3.1philliplimss14.png"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1037" alt="3.1philliplimss14" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/3.1philliplimss14.png" width="440" height="498" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/VERAWANGSS14.png"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1038" alt="VERAWANGSS14" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/VERAWANGSS14.png" width="433" height="540" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong><em>Guido Palau for ALEXANDER WANG:</em></strong>Guido surprised us a little bit with such a loose texture for AWANG this season, but loved the matte texture + center part.<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/Alexanderwangss14.png"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1039" alt="Alexanderwangss14" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/Alexanderwangss14.png" width="451" height="641" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<em><strong>Eugene Souleiman for DONNA KARAN:</strong></em> Sleek, structured hair, half back {hi 90''s!} + zero volume. Classic<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/DONNAKARANss14.png"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1036" alt="DONNAKARANss14" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/DONNAKARANss14.png" width="449" height="570" /></a><em><strong>Jen Atkin for FALLON:</strong></em> Beautiful messy, undone texture, accessorized with hair jewelry giving the hair peeks of metal, really cool.<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/fallonss14.png"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1040" alt="fallonss14" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/fallonss14.png" width="423" height="370" /></a>\r\n\r\nOverall, really loving + inspired with all of the looks thus far. I love when artists take a really natural approach to styling + create something unique around it, whether it be the texture, finish, or accessory. Always a good time to get inspired + push me to try new things... X', 'NYFW Hair Trends: five favorites from new york fashion week', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1035-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-01-27 10:19:10', '2015-01-27 10:19:10', '', 1035, 'http://182.71.22.42/sarah/?p=1852', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
