(1858, 1, '2015-01-27 10:52:43', '2015-01-27 10:52:43', '<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/IMG_7628.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1835" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/IMG_7628.jpg" alt="IMG_7628" width="1844" height="1280" /></a>I cannot believe it is 2015! How time flies. + Not only 2015, but it is indeed two weeks in. I took some time this weekend to reflect on all of the goodness, hardships, ups, downs, + memories from last year. Better late than never I suppose. So many life changing moments; I got to celebrate engagements, weddings, new babies, I had the most incredible opportunities to work with beautiful, + crazy talented people. At the end of the year, I felt fulfilled. What a joy to share in the lives of such beautiful people. Thank you to all who have contributed greatly to last year! Some of my favorite moments...<!--more-->\r\n\r\n<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/2015_2014_IN_REVIEW_POST_02.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1787" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/2015_2014_IN_REVIEW_POST_02.jpg" alt="2015_2014_IN_REVIEW_POST_02" width="1280" height="853" /></a> <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/2015_2014_IN_REVIEW_POST_03.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1788" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/2015_2014_IN_REVIEW_POST_03.jpg" alt="2015_2014_IN_REVIEW_POST_03" width="2506" height="2680" /></a> <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/2015_2014_IN_REVIEW_POST_04.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1789" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/2015_2014_IN_REVIEW_POST_04.jpg" alt="2015_2014_IN_REVIEW_POST_04" width="3776" height="2062" /></a> <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/2015_2014_IN_REVIEW_POST_05.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image