(1861, 1, '2015-01-27 10:59:41', '2015-01-27 10:59:41', '<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_ModTest_SARAH_KEHOE_HEIDI_VERSTER_ISAAC_WEBER_3.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1657" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_ModTest_SARAH_KEHOE_HEIDI_VERSTER_ISAAC_WEBER_3.jpg" alt="2014_ModTest_SARAH_KEHOE_HEIDI_VERSTER_ISAAC_WEBER_3" width="3840" height="5760" /></a>A new cute editorial story; Heidi Verster + Isaac Weber are two faves of mine! We were telling the story of two mod lovebirds running around Brooklyn... It was a fun day with a lovely crew.<!--more-->\r\n\r\nWe were all inspired by a 60''s feel, I kept Heidi''s skin really bright using <a href="http://www.chanel.com/en_US/fragrance-beauty/Makeup-Base-LE-BLANC-DE-CHANEL-138459/sku/138460" target="_blank">Le Blanc De Chanel.</a> It is a multi use luminating cream, I often use after moisturizing, before foundation. Of course, Brigitte Bardot was famous for her sexy winged liner, which I recreated here using <a href="http://www.bobbibrowncosmetics.com/product/2328/7785/Makeup/Eyes/Eyeliner/Long-Wear-Gel-Eyeliner/index.tmpl#i.p9htwr26adbv10" target="_blank">Bobbi Brown''s Long-Wear Gel Eyeliner in Black Ink.</a> I softened the top of the liner with my fingers slightly, to make for a more modern look.<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_ModTest_SARAH_KEHOE_HEIDI_VERSTER_ISAAC_WEBER_1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1656" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_ModTest_SARAH_KEHOE_HEIDI_VERSTER_ISAAC_WEBER_1.jpg" alt="2014_ModTest_SARAH_KEHOE_HEIDI_VERSTER_ISAAC_WEBER_1" width="1938" height="1500" /></a> <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_ModTest_SARAH_KEHOE_HEIDI_VERSTER_ISAAC_WEBER_6.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1660" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_ModTest_SARAH_KEHOE_HEIDI_VERS