(1866, 1, '2015-01-27 11:04:00', '2015-01-27 11:04:00', 'I have gone on the hunt lately to find some new seasonal must haves. If you keep up with this blog, you know what a fan I am of changing your look with the season. I have put together a few new favorites, that are seasonally appropriate as the colors + temperatures are changing...<!--more-->I love a good bronzer set. But! Away with the shimmery bronzers, Miami tan look. I love this new Flushed palette in Strip by Urban Decay. It has a beautiful bronzer which I use for contour, a highlighter I place above my cheekbones + browbones + a pretty, cool toned, pink blush for a touch on the apples of my cheek.<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/2014_BLOG_FALL_FAVORITES_ARMANI_MAC_ANASTASIA_NAKED_5.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1710" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/2014_BLOG_FALL_FAVORITES_ARMANI_MAC_ANASTASIA_NAKED_5.jpg" alt="2014_BLOG_FALL_FAVORITES_ARMANI_MAC_ANASTASIA_NAKED_5" width="3460" height="1995" /></a> After a summer of brushed through soft brows, I am stepping up the structure with Anastasia Beverly Hills Dipbrow Pomade. Using an angle liner brush I take a small amount [a little goes a long way!] + making tiny brush strokes in an upwards motion to create a natural effect. Then wisping around the top edges of brown to create arch. I love the tone of Taupe, so beautiful, a great ashy option for blondes/dirty blondes.<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1711" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/2014_BLOG_FALL_FAVORITES_ARMANI_MAC_ANASTASIA_NAKED_6.jpg" alt="2014_BLOG_FALL_FAVORITES_ARMANI_MAC_ANASTASIA_NAKED_6" width="3049" height="1514" />The quickest way to get a polished look quickly is to pop a lip. Here are my new favorite fall must have lipsticks. From left to right:\r\n\r\nMAC Cosmetics Matte in <a href="http://www.maccosmetics.com/product/shaded/168/310/Lipstick/index.tmpl" target="_blank">So Chaud</a> [what i am wearing in the photo above]\r\n\r\nArmani <a href="http://www.giorgioarmanibeauty-usa.com/on/demandware.store/Sites-armani_us-Site/default/Product-Show?pid=A439&amp;bookmark=363243" target="_blank">Rouge Ecstasy in 404</a>\r\n\r\nMAC Cosmetics <a href="http://www.maccosmetics.com/product/shaded/13432/310/New-Collections/The-Matte-Lip/Lips/Lipstick/index.tmpl" target="_blank">Flat Out Fabulous</a>\r\n\r\nA poppy, orangy red, classic red + a bright berry.<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/2014_BLOG_FALL_FAVORITES_ARMANI_MAC_ANASTASIA_NAKED_4.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1709" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/2014_BLOG_FALL_FAVORITES_ARMANI_MAC_ANASTASIA_NAKED_4.jpg" alt="2014_BLOG_FALL_FAVORITES_ARMANI_MAC_ANASTASIA_NAKED_4" width="3420" height="2166" /></a>Here is to layers + hot drinks + crisp neighborhood strolls.. X', 'USE: A Few Favorites for Fall', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1705-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-01-27 11:04:00', '2015-01-27 11:04:00', '', 1705, 'http://182.71.22.42/sarah/?p=1866', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
