(1875, 1, '2015-01-27 11:15:59', '2015-01-27 11:15:59', '<iframe style="border: none;" src="http://abcnews.go.com/video/embed?id=25569286" width="640" height="360" scrolling="no"></iframe>\r\n<a href="http://abcnews.go.com/video">More ABC news videos</a> | <a href="http://abcnews.go.com/international">Latest world news</a>\r\n\r\nWednesday [VERY early morning] I headed up to the Good Morning America studios to paint the faces of UK electronic group, Clean Bandit. They all have a structured yet effortless style... <!--more-->\r\n\r\nFor the gals, it was all about dewy skin, fresh + natural with feathery lashes. I used Armani Beauty Fluid Master Primer as a base + then buffed the Fluid Sheers [5+8] over cheeks + t zone as a base. That gives the skin a gorgeous glow. For the brows I used Armani Brow Defining Pencils.<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/CLEAN_BANDIT_ARMANI_BEAUTY_SARAH_APPLEBY.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1645" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/CLEAN_BANDIT_ARMANI_BEAUTY_SARAH_APPLEBY.jpg" alt="CLEAN_BANDIT_ARMANI_BEAUTY_SARAH_APPLEBY" width="3053" height="1617" /></a>\r\n\r\nThe girls [+ guys!] were a pleasure to work with! Can''t wait to see what happens for them next. X', 'NEW WORK: Clean Bandit performs on Good Morning America!', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1643-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-01-27 11:15:59', '2015-01-27 11:15:59', '', 1643, 'http://182.71.22.42/sarah/?p=1875', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
