(1879, 1, '2015-01-27 11:17:39', '2015-01-27 11:17:39', 'The last few weeks I have been working with French designer, Alix Petit, on her presentation for Heimstone''s latest collection: Imperial Summer 2015. Last nite, it all came to life at French establishment, Laduree, in Soho. Only fitting that one of my favorite French skincare brand, <a href="http://us.caudalie.com/" target="_blank">Caudalie</a> came on board to sponsor the event. I had an amazing team of girls that helped me bring Alix''s Safari influence + new collection to life with beautifully contoured + sunkissed skin...Â <!--more-->\r\n\r\n<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_HEIMSTONE_SUMMER_PRESENTATION_MAKEUP_BTS_03.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1667" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_HEIMSTONE_SUMMER_PRESENTATION_MAKEUP_BTS_03.jpg" alt="2014_HEIMSTONE_SUMMER_PRESENTATION_MAKEUP_BTS_03" width="2880" height="1789" /></a>When talking about a Safari, I immediately think of sun kissed + glowy skin. To begin prepping the girls, I used a very generous amount of the <a href="http://us.caudalie.com/organic-grape-water.html" target="_blank">Caudalie Grape Water spray</a> which soothes + moisturizes the skin, following with <a href="http://us.caudalie.com/shop-products/concern-1/dark-spot-correction/radiance-serum-complexion-correcting.html" target="_blank">Radiance Serum</a> all over the face. Then onto <a href="http://uk.caudalie.com/broad-spectrum-sfp20-anti-wrinkle-protect-fluid.html" target="_blank">Broad Spectrum SPF20 Anti-Wrinkle Protect Fluid</a>. Any cream with SPF in it will give the skin a slight glow due to the zinc. I love this new product, it has grape polyphenols in it, known to fight free radicals [free radicals are found to be responsible for 80% of wrinkles].<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1682" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_HEIMSTONE_SUMMER_PRESENTATION_MAKEUP_BTS_19.jpg" alt="Processed with VSCOcam with f2 preset" width="3264" height="2176" />\r\n\r\nIt was all about body too. <a href="http://us.caudalie.com/vine-body-butter-1.html" target="_blank">Caudalie''s Vine Body Butter</a> nourishes + repairs the skin, then to finish legs, arms + dÃ©colletage I sprayed the <a href="http://us.caudalie.com/divine-oil.html" target="_blank">Divine Oil</a> on the girls.Â <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_HEIMSTONE_SUMMER_PRESENTATION_MAKEUP_BTS_18.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-1681 size-full" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_HEIMSTONE_SUMMER_PRESENTATION_MAKEUP_BTS_18-e1414077616566.jpg" alt="Processed with VSCOcam with f2 preset" width="2448" height="1958" /></a>For makeup I did an obvious warm brown creamy contour on the eyes, sharp brows with a beautiful brow highlight. My favorite trick for highlighting skin without sparkles or shimmer is to use <a href="http://us.caudalie.com/premier-cru-the-eye-cream-1.html" target="_blank">Caudalie''s Premier Cru, The Eye Cream</a>. Using fingers to pat it below brow + through the c-section on the top of the cheekbones.Â  All the girls lips were a nude berry. To finish the look, I sprayed the famous <a href="http://us.caudalie.com/beauty-elixir-full-size.html" target="_blank">Beauty Elixir</a> to set the makeup + finish the skin with a radiant glow.<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_HEIMSTONE_SUMMER_PRESENTATION_MAKEUP_BTS_17.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1680" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_HEIMSTONE_SUMMER_PRESENTATION_MAKEUP_BTS_17.jpg" alt="2014_HEIMSTONE_SUMMER_PRESENTATION_MAKEUP_BTS_17" width="3264" height="2176" /></a>Â Alix + her twin sister Caroline, along with the beauties of Heimstone outside of Laduree before the presentation started. Â <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/2014_HEIMSTONE_SUMMER