(1901, 1, '2015-01-27 11:36:04', '2015-01-27 11:36:04', 'Well, I love being on the beach. Especially amidst one of the longest winters in NYC! I had a big birthday last month + my Mother flew from Edmonton, Canada to treat me to the prettiest beach vacation {I KNOW!}. We did it all; climbed waterfalls, snorkeled, visited coffee + cocoa plantations, cliff jumped, rode horses, drank delicious cocktails out of coconuts, jumped in a blue lagoon, moto rides, explored caves, shared stories with locals, swam, boat rides, + more. Here are a few of my favorite snaps from the trip...<!--more--><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1548" alt="IMG_9532" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/IMG_9532.jpg" width="2448" height="1632" /> <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/IMG_9551.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1549" alt="IMG_9551" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/IMG_9551.jpg" width="3240" height="2083" /></a> <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/IMG_9582.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1550" alt="IMG_9582" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/IMG_9582.jpg" width="3234" height="1621" /></a> <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/L1010806.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1551" alt="L1010806" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/L1010806.jpg" width="3697" height="2350" /></a> <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/L1010807.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1552" alt="L1010807" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/L1010807.jpg" width="3485" height="2025" /></a><a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/L1010832.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1556" alt="L1010832" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/L1010832.jpg" width="3662" he