(1914, 1, '2015-01-27 12:10:09', '2015-01-27 12:10:09', '&nbsp;\r\n\r\nYesterday I had the pleasure of painting the faces of Amy Heidemann + Nick Noonan of the pop duo: <a href="http://www.karminmusic.com/us/biography" target="_blank"><em>KARMIN,</em></a> for the March Issue of <em><a href="http://flattmag.com/" target="_blank">FLATT magazine</a></em>. It was shot by the amazing, <a href="http://kelseybennett.com/#img_72610028-copy" target="_blank"><em>Kelsey Bennett</em> </a>+ styled by Fashion Director, <em><a href="https://twitter.com/Ashley_Pruitt" target="_blank">Ashley Priutt</a>.</em> Here are some snaps from the day...<!--more--> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1447" alt="karminsarahappleby5" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/karminsarahappleby5.jpg" width="3264" height="2448" />Amy is known for her retro glam style, lots of winged liner, big bold lips + rockabilly rolls in the hair. We went for a little something different yesterday. Her bone structure lends to natural makeup- she is beautiful. I chose a creamy, subtle contoured lid with really textured but still natural feeling, feathery lashes. Then a full structured brow to frame it all. We did a diffused/smudgy red lip, keeping the saturation in the center + diffusing out {how to blog coming next week!}. Skin prep using <em><a href="http://www.murad.com/?XID=A10109&amp;affilnet=cj" target="_blank">Murad</a></em> + color <a href="http://www.clinique.com/cms/product/supercat/makeup.tmpl" target="_blank"><em>Clinique</em></a>. Damien Monzillo did the hair, seventies inspired sexy, tousled tresses..<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1442" alt="karminsarahappleby" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/karminsarahappleby.jpg" width="2616" height="1742" /><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1446" alt="karminsarahappleby4" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/karminsarahappleby4.jpg" width="3264" height="2448" /> We were shooting in this incredible townhouse in the west village, this was the wallpaper in the bathroom- it was foiled!<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1448" alt="karminsarahappleby6" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/karminsarahappleby6.jpg" width="2448" height="1836" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1444" alt="karminsarahappleby2" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/karminsarahappleby2.jpg" width="3264" height="2448" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1443" alt="karminsarahappleby1" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/karminsarahappleby1.jpg" width="2448" height="1836" /> It is always fun working with musicians, Amy + Nick are such gems, I can''t wait to see what happens when they debut their first album in a few months! + Will be posting final layout of the shoot when it gets to print... X', 'BEHIND THE SCENES/ FLATT magazine shoot with band duo KARMIN', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1441-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-01-27 12:10:09', '2015-01-27 12:10:09', '', 1441, 'http://182.71.22.42/sarah/?p=1914', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
