(1976, 1, '2015-01-28 05:54:16', '2015-01-28 05:54:16', 'I had the pleasure of heading up a serious A-TEAM, doing both hair + makeup on 16 talent for the VMA promo video this year. So premise is a bunch of Gaga''s Little Monsters getting all crazy, running around rooftops in BK tagging + posting Gaga paraphernalia with the tag- no sleep until Brooklyn {which is when she will perform on the show this weekend!}. I was in for creating some pretty strong/visually impacting {!} hair styles + makeup...\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\nFor makeup it was all meant to be graphic + strong {dare I say it, Chola + Gaga were the inspiration}, these Little Monsters mean business. SO some gals had the Chola feel, some had the new art pop Gaga feel. Hair was very structured, young, + playful. A few shots of the styling...\r\n\r\n<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/btsladygaga.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-947" alt="btsladygaga" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/btsladygaga.jpg" width="3055" height="2182" /></a> <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/btsgaga12.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-939" alt="btsgaga12" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/btsgaga12.jpg" width="2537" height="1812" /></a> <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/btsgaga11.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-937" alt="btsgaga11" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/btsgaga11.jpg" width="3264" height="2448" /></a> <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/btsgaga10.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-942" alt="btsgaga10" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/btsgaga10.jpg" width="2498" height="1784" /></a>\r\n\r\nGents working away...<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-938" alt="btsgaga8" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/btsgaga8.jpg" width="2449" height="1749" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-936" alt="btsgaga7" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/btsgaga7.jpg" width="2990" height="2136" />We shot right next to the Williamsburg bridge, look at the sunset at the beginning of the work day {6p!}.<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-946" alt="btsgaga2" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/btsgaga2.jpg" width="2448" height="3264" />Mid eve... <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-945" alt="btsgaga5" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/btsgaga5.jpg" width="3035" height="2168" /><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-940" alt="btsgaga9" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/btsgaga9.jpg" width="2294" height="1639" /><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-944" alt="btsgaga4" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/btsgaga4.jpg" width="3192" height="2280" />Above, they had a street artist do the No Sleep, only had one take to do so!  <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-935" alt="btsgaga6" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/btsgaga6.jpg" width="2747" height="1962" /> This is my major amazing team. Thank you to you gals+guys for a big job well done...<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/photo.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-955" alt="photo" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/photo.jpg" width="2982" height="1986" /></a><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-943" alt="btsgaga3" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/btsgaga3.jpg" width="3041" height="2172" />+ Then the sun rose, home to bed after a long nite of beauty. I love being a part of these creative jobs. It stretches me to try new techniques + products. Can''t wait to show you the final video tomorrow! X', 'BEHIND THE SCENES: No sleep until Gaga', '', 'inherit', 'open', 