(1983, 1, '2015-01-28 05:57:03', '2015-01-28 05:57:03', ' With the summer temperatures on high all month long, it is so important to keep hydrated. Here are a few of my favorite ways to not only feel hydrated but look it too...<!--more-->\r\n\r\nNumero Uno is H2O. I can''t get enough water, especially when I am running around in the heat. I find I drink so much more of it when I am drinking out of a straw, I love this <a href="http://www.amazon.com/Aladdin-20-Ounce-To-Tumbler-Clear/dp/B004Y3E40Q/ref=sr_1_3?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1375457769&amp;sr=8-3&amp;keywords=water+cup+with+straw+and+lid" target="_blank">water cup</a> I found on Amazon. I typically will add a few slices of cucumber or lemon to spruce it up.\r\n\r\nI am a huge fan of Jurlique products, especially the <a href="http://www.jurlique.com/products/r06/rose-body-oil" target="_blank">Rose Body Oil</a>. Jurlique works with all natural products, why I am convinced it works so well for everything your skin really needs. Straight after a bath or shower, I generously put it all over my body. Not only does it smell delightful + floral, but it leaves a pretty sheen too.\r\n\r\n<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-897" alt="jurliquehydration" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/jurliquehydration.jpg" width="3116" height="2250" />My new favorite lip product is from C.O.Bigelow. The <a href="http://www.bigelowchemists.com/c-o-bigelow-lemon-lip-cream-no-1420.html" target="_blank">Lemon Citron Lip Cream</a>. It is made from 100% lemon oil, + natural products to hydrate your lips. The cream also gives a nude tint to your lips, perfect for summer.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/glossylips.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-898" alt="glossylips" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/glossylips.jpg" width="1148" height="829" /></a>A little trick: the Lip Cream does not need to be limited to your lips, I love to place it with my finger on the brow bone + tops of my cheek bone for a pretty, dewy glow. Over top of that I will spritz <a href="http://www.skinstore.com/p-2872-skyn-iceland-arctic-face-mist-with-multivitamin-complex.aspx" target="_blank">Skyn''s Arctic Face Mist</a> which has loads of vitamins to tone + moisturize your skin whilst on the go...<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-899" alt="cobigelowhighlight" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/cobigelowhighlight.jpg" width="1087" height="785" />That''s all I need for a happy, hydrated summer, now if I could just make a beach appear near my brooklyn condo for daily dips! X\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Hydration: Beat the Heat!', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '896-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-01-28 05:57:03', '2015-01-28 05:57:03', '', 896, 'http://182.71.22.42/sarah/?p=1983', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
