(1985, 1, '2015-01-28 05:57:39', '2015-01-28 05:57:39', 'I work with many beautiful guys + gals, it''s a pleasure {most of the time!} to work in such an intimate capacity with complete strangers. As I work on so many different models, I see such complexity in the structure of the face. Cheekbones, hairline, lips, brow bone, nose, chin, jawline, eyes, skin color, texture, are just a few things that set us apart. Here are a few new faces I would like to get my hands {+brushes} on...<!--more-->\r\n\r\n<em>GRACE MAHARY:</em> Edmonton, Canada\r\n\r\nThis face! She hails from my hometown, Edmonton... So have to love her. She has a beautiful, symmetrical hairline, gorgeous cheekbones, + thin/wide brows that map what could be my favorite thick + structured brow, all highlighted by her prominent browbone. Gah! What a beauty.<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Screen-shot-2013-07-30-at-10.12.36-PM.png"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-889" alt="Screen shot 2013-07-30 at 10.12.36 PM" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Screen-shot-2013-07-30-at-10.12.36-PM.png" width="815" height="658" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<em>IRINA LISS:Â </em>from Lukhovitsy, Russia\r\n\r\nI love her thin face, natural brows + straight nose. She has a beautiful complexion, can''t wait to see where she goes.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Screen-shot-2013-07-30-at-9.30.45-PM.png"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-884" alt="Screen shot 2013-07-30 at 9.30.45 PM" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Screen-shot-2013-07-30-at-9.30.45-PM.png" width="573" height="662" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<em>Eleanor Hayes</em>: London England\r\n\r\nEleanor has an interesting look. I love the freckles, interesting hairline + plump lips. This photo does not do her beauty justice..\r\n\r\n<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/eleanorhayes1.png"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-886" alt="eleanorhayes" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/eleanorhayes1.png" width="579" height="655" /></a>\r\n\r\n<em>Marikka Juhler</em>: Hammelev, Denmark\r\n\r\nLove Marikka''s thin brows, bright eyes + heart shaped lips. I would love to see her with bleached brows + a deep red lipstick. Perfection.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Screen-shot-2013-07-30-at-9.50.29-PM.png"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-887" alt="Screen shot 2013-07-30 at 9.50.29 PM" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Screen-shot-2013-07-30-at-9.50.29-PM.png" width="561" height="654" /></a>\r\n\r\n<em>Chiharu:</em> Japan\r\n\r\nWith razo sharp cheekbones, strong jawline + full lips, this one has already won the likes of Stella McCartney, Chanel + is currently featured in an editorial for Vogue Japan. She is one to watch! <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Screen-shot-2013-07-30-at-10.04.53-PM.png"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-888" alt="Screen shot 2013-07-30 at 10.04.53 PM" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Screen-shot-2013-07-30-at-10.04.53-PM.png" width="674" height="634" /></a>\r\n\r\nAlthough I apply makeup for a living, I just love clean skin, when the natural features are the focus. A bare face is quite striking. However, when done properly, makeup will be your best friend to enhance it all. X\r\n\r\n*These photos are not my own, pulled from various fashion sites, shot by unknown photographers.', 'Some new faces I would like to paint.', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '883-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-01-28 05:57:39', '2015-01-28 05:57:39', '', 883, 'http://182.71.22.42/sarah/?p=1985', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
