(2016, 1, '2015-01-28 06:13:58', '2015-01-28 06:13:58', 'I have really fine hair, but lots of it. I have learned throughout years of styling hair, that although I''d like a little wave or a little more hair- I can do more with this texture than most {it''s flexible!}. Whatever your hair type, learn to work with it. You''ll find it will respond to different products + styling tools differently; so if you aren''t getting the results you want, switch it up! Here''s my step by step from just out of the shower + squeaky clean, fine hair...<!--more--><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-729" alt="phytovolume" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/phytovolume.jpg" width="4249" height="2832" />When your hair is towel dried {no need to make your hair or the product work harder than it has to} I spray a generous amount of <a href="http://www.sephora.com/phytovolume-actif-volumizing-spray-P2910?skuId=1512334" target="_blank">Phytovolume Actif Volumizing Spray</a> into my roots + work into the hair.<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-730" alt="salontechdryer" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/salontechdryer.jpg" width="4416" height="2944" />Then I use my <a href="http://www.folica.com/tools/hair-dryers/salon-tech-2800-featherlight-hair-dryer" target="_blank">Salontech Featherweight Blow dryer</a> {beware: it gets really hot! But good for less time on your hair} along with my <a href="http://www.sephora.com/large-round-brush-P241317?om_mmc=Googlepla,_requestid=42976,cm_mmc=us_search-_-GG-_-pla-_-,ci_src=17588969,ci_sku=1170489" target="_blank">Large Round Brush from Sephora</a> + take sections of 1.5in to blow dry at a time, really focusing on the roots + getting a lift.<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-731" alt="sephoraroundbrush" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/sephoraroundbrush.jpg" width="4416" height="2944" />I spray about four pumps of my favorite <a href="http://www.davines.com/en/products/view/sea-salt" target="_blank">Davines Sea Salt Primer</a> {for wizards thank you!} into the body of my hair + rub in with my fingers creating friction + texture.<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-728" alt="hairproducts" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/hairproducts.jpg" width="2110" height="2110" />Tada! Products above, {they are all used!} it''s all you need for some messy textured hair... X<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-733" alt="texturedhair2" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/texturedhair2.jpg" width="3705" height="2470" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'HAIR/ how to: texture+mess with oh so fine hair ', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '734-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-01-28 06:13:58', '2015-01-28 06:13:58', '', 734, 'http://182.71.22.42/sarah/?p=2016', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(2017, 1, '2015-01-28 06:14:23', '2015-01-28 06:14:23', 'Part Deux! When I spent the <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/hair-how-to-megan-james-of-purity-ring/" target="_blank">afternoon with Megan</a> two weeks back, along with hair we did some pretty Spring makeup. Megan''s au natural during the day + some eyeliner by nite. I wanted to play up her light brown eyes + milky skin, here''s what we did...<!--more-->\r\n\r\nTo prep her {pretty much flawless} skin I used Jurlique Radiance Serum with a generous amount of Jurlique Herbal Recovery Eye Cream around her eyes + tops of her cheeks. I put some Reve de Miel Lip Balm on her lips + applied NARS Sheer Foundation which gives the perfect amount of coverage + a beautiful glowy texture to the skin. With the foundation I concentrated the application to the center of her face where she has minimal redness + then buffing it out to the outer edges.<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-706" alt="MJSAjurliquenars" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/MJSAjurliquenars.jpg" width="3264" height="2176" /> Our beauty before...<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-709" alt="meganjamessarahappleby6" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/meganjamessarahappleby6.jpg" width="2319" height="1546" /> <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/narsstilaclinique.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-710" alt="narsstilaclinique" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/narsstilaclinique.jpg" width="3264" height="2174" /></a> â€¢Eyes/ Lined the top of her lids with <a href="http://www.maccosmetics.com/product/shaded/151/476/Products/Eyes/Liner/Powerpoint-Eye-Pencil/index.tmpl" target="_blank">MAC''s Powerpoint Pencil</a> in Out to Sea + blended it out with a firm synthetic brush. Added <a href="http://www.narscosmetics.com/color/eyes/larger-than-life-long-wear-eyeliner/barrow-street" target="_blank">NARS Larger Than Life Long-Wear Eyeliner</a> in Seafoam Green to the inner corner top + bottom. Again, blendedÂ  together with the darker, stronger teal. I focused the seafoam color on the bottom of her lashes. Applied <a href="http://www.stilacosmetics.com/product/glamoureyes-mascara.do" target="_blank">Stila glamoureyes mascara</a> giving volume + definition.\r\n\r\nâ€¢Eyebrows/ Megan has such great big brows! I love the <a href="http://www.clinique.com/product/1595/4799/Makeup/Brows/Brow-Keeper/index.tmpl" target="_blank">Clinique Brow Keeper in Honey</a> + built in some shape for a more structured look. Then used the other end of the pencil to brush up the eyebrows to open her eyes a little more.\r\n\r\nâ€¢Lips/ The new <a href="http://www.stilacosmetics.com/product/color+balm+lipstick.do?sortby=ourPicks&amp;page=2" target="_blank">Stila Color Balm lipsticks</a> are the perfect amount of saturation. Gabrielle is a nudey pink which suited Meg''s looks perfectly.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/meganjamessarahappleby21.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-703" alt="meganjamessarahappleby2" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/meganjamessarahappleby21.jpg" width="3264" height="2174" /></a><a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/meganjamessarahappleby7.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-708" alt="meganjamessarahappleby7" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/meganjamessarahappleby7.jpg" width="3264" height="2174" /></a><a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/meganjamessarahappleby8.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-705" alt="meganjamessarahappleby8" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/meganjamessarahappleby8.jpg" width="3264" height="2174" /></a>+ Voila! A poppy teal eye + subtle everything else makes for the perfect Summer day-to-eve look. Love this gal. X<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/meganjamessarahappleby5.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-713" alt="meganjamessarahappleby" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/meganjamessarahappleby5.jpg" width="3264" height="2176" /></a>', 'Makeup: How to/ megan james of purity ring', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '702-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-01-28 06:14:23', '2015-01-28 06:14:23', '', 702, 'http://182.71.22.42/sarah/?p=2017', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(2018, 1, '2015-01-28 06:14:55', '2015-01-28 06:14:55', 'It was five years ago today I packed up all of my belongings into 4 big boxes, 2 suitcases + left Vancouver, BC. It was five years ago that I felt anxious, nervous, scared, excited, liberated, crazy + free arriving in the big city starting everything new...<!--more-->\r\n\r\nI have been so blessed to have met the incredible people I have in my life here. It''s been a gift building a beautiful community of people I love who encourage + support me in the best times + hardest times. Getting to work with the most talented people in the industry; painting the most beautiful faces, meeting dynamic + inspiring people that make me want to be more + indulging in the most delicious restaurants + bars; makes me so incredibly thankful for my time here.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/NYILY1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-688" alt="NYILY1" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/NYILY1.jpg" width="901" height="901" /></a> <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/NYILY.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-689" alt="NYILY" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/NYILY.jpg" width="1280" height="1280" /></a> <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/NYILY3.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-690" alt="NYILY3" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/NYILY3.jpg" width="819" height="819" /></a>Â  <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/NYILY7.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-693" alt="NYILY7" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/NYILY7.jpg" width="960" height="960" /></a><a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/NYILY4.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-691" alt="NYILY4" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/NYILY4.jpg" width="960" height="960" /></a> + To think there''s more! More dinner parties, crazy photoshoots, sunrises, late nite walks, long summer nites, beach trips, restaurant hops, + ETC! I can''t wait to see what the next 5 bring... Dear New York: I love you!', '5 Years/ Happy Anniversary New York!', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '687-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-01-28 06:14:55', '2015-01-28 06:14:55', '', 687, 'http://182.71.22.42/sarah/?p=2018', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(2019, 1, '2015-01-28 06:15:45', '2015-01-28 06:15:45', 'Here''s the new beauty editorial I did for <a href="http://beautyhigh.com/" target="_blank">Beauty High</a>! Loved the team so much. Very fun being on jobs where all I do is hang out in a candy shop + play with color on pretty girls...<!--more--><a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/COTL_COVER.png"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-673" alt="COTL_COVER" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/COTL_COVER.png" width="1027" height="770" /></a><a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/COTL_SLIDE-5.png"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-677" alt="COTL_SLIDE-5" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/COTL_SLIDE-5.png" width="1027" height="770" /></a><a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/COTL_SLIDE-2.png"><a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/COTL_SLIDE-6.png"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-678" alt="COTL_SLIDE-6" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/COTL_SLIDE-6.png" width="1027" height="770" /></a><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-675" alt="COTL_SLIDE-2" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/COTL_SLIDE-2.png" width="1027" height="770" /></a><a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/COTL_CREDITS.png"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-674" alt="COTL_CREDITS" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/COTL_CREDITS.png" width="1027" height="770" /></a>Check out the <a href="http://beautyhigh.com/colored-hair-get-inspired-color-outside-the-lines/" target="_blank">full story</a> on Beauty High''s website, with my personal notes about the choices I made for makeup on the girls!', 'New Work/ coloring for beauty high', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '672-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-01-28 06:15:45', '2015-01-28 06:15:45', '', 672, 'http://182.71.22.42/sarah/?p=2019', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(2020, 1, '2015-01-28 06:16:02', '2015-01-28 06:16:02', 'The last two weeks I have barely slept a wink past 630a + although at times I think my body could use a little more sleep, I will rise + take full advantage of the quiet. Being a morning person- a real one {!} I have become really good at making the most of the early hours.Â  Summer is near + I just set up my little bistro set on my balcony; I have a feeling many early mornings will be spent here...<!--more-->\r\n\r\n<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/davidstea.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-662" alt="davidstea" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/davidstea.jpg" width="2874" height="1916" /></a>I made some loose leaf <a href="http://www.davidstea.com/bravissimo-en?&amp;currid=usd&amp;LN=EN" target="_blank">David''s Tea in Bravissimo</a>, it''s the yummiest herbal infusion of chamomile/rosehip/gojiberries/orangepeel/peppermint.\r\n\r\nReading through <a href="http://www.amazon.com/Carine-Roitfeld-Irreverent/dp/0847833682" target="_blank">Carine Roitfeld''s Irreverent</a>, I know I am a little late on this one- but better late than never! I have a long love affair with Paris + the parisian culture, this book is not only visually beautiful but full of Carine''s musings about the Fashion industry, work, France, + all things beautiful. J''adore!\r\n\r\n<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/whitenails.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-663" alt="whitenails" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/whitenails.jpg" width="2824" height="1883" /></a>I paint my nails white. I have been using <a href="http://www.bloom.com/sephora-by-opi-nail-colour-white-hot.html" target="_blank">Sephora by Oâ€¢Pâ€¢I in White Hot</a>. It''s a stark white that lasts. I love freshly painted nails + when I don''t have time to make it to get a mani, I make it work!<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/whitehotopisephora.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-664" alt="whitehotopisephora" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/whitehotopisephora.jpg" width="2885" height="1923" /></a>\r\n\r\nWhile listening to <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Haim_%28band%29" target="_blank">Haim</a> I am thankful for the prettiest view of Brooklyn, the trees are lush + full of life. It''s going to be a good day... Now off to take Little White Lightening {my vintage Peugeot} to Williamsburg to meet the gals! X', 'Early Mornings/ + some favorite things', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '660-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-01-28 06:16:02', '2015-01-28 06:16:02', '', 660, 'http://182.71.22.42/sarah/?p=2020', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(2021, 1, '2015-01-28 06:17:07', '2015-01-28 06:17:07', 'Yesterday I spent the afternoon with my dear friend Megan {we spent our summers at her family''s lake house in Alberta Canada!}, chatting + laughing + playing pretty. She + brilliant man, Corin Roddick, make up the duo <a href="http://thepurityring.tumblr.com/" target="_blank">Purity Ring</a>. It''s been so much fun watching her + her career move, not to mention I am a huge fan of their <a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/artist/purity-ring/id461030854" target="_blank">music</a>. She is known for her crazy, big, toussled hair, so after I gently passed on a few ''take care of your hair'' tips, we played...<!--more-->\r\n\r\n<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/tigibandbdavines.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-651" alt="tigibandbdavines" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/tigibandbdavines.jpg" width="3058" height="2040" /></a>Megan loves her hair with crazy texture, she hadn''t washed her hair in 2 days, which is perfect for styling. I started by combing through her hair + spraying in <a href="http://www.catwalkbytigi.com/the-catwalk-collection/styling-collection/session-series-styling-collection/transforming-dry-shampoo" target="_blank">Catwalk Transforming Dry Shampoo</a> generously in her roots + throughout the body of her hair. This will soak up any natural oils + turn it to matte texture. Then I separated her hair with clips in 4 horizontal sections, leaving the bottom section out. I sprayed <a href="http://www.bumbleandbumble.com/product/73/193/Products/Styling/Sprays/does-it-all-styling-spray/index.tmpl" target="_blank">Bumble and bumble does it All Styling Spray</a> throughout to help set.Â <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/meganjameshair2.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-649" alt="meganjameshair2" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/meganjameshair2.jpg" width="3264" height="2176" /></a>\r\n\r\nI used a flatiron to straighten the bottom 4 inches of her hair. Using a 1 inch curling iron I wrapped 1.5 inch sections, not using the clamp, around the iron in all different directions. *Depending on the way you hold your iron, horizontally or vertically, will give you a different finish. As well, which side you wrap the hair from. This will give it our desired messy, textured look... Here is the hair set: Â  <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/maganjameshair.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-647" alt="maganjameshair" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/maganjameshair.jpg" width="3264" height="2176" /></a>I left her hair for about 30 minutes {to do makeup! That How to is next week!}, + then flipped her hair over + shook it all up. We love that she is not afraid to go big! Finishing off the ends I put in <a href="http://www.davines.com/en/products/view/finest-oil-non-oil-n1" target="_blank">Davines Finest Oil Non Oil</a>, for wizards! This is the best oil, it brings the hair together to give it a dirty, natural look. Megan is a total babe + she owns her big hair, so much fun to play with this...<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/meganjameshairSA.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-652" alt="meganjameshairSA" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/meganjameshairSA.jpg" width="2448" height="3264" /></a> <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/meganjamessarahappleby2.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-653" alt="meganjamessarahappleby" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/meganjamessarahappleby2.jpg" width="3003" height="2002" /></a>More to come.... X', 'Hair: How To/ megan james of Purity Ring', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '644-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-01-28 06:17:07', '2015-01-28 06:17:07', '', 644, 'http://182.71.22.42/sarah/?p=2021', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
