(2023, 1, '2015-01-28 06:17:59', '2015-01-28 06:17:59', 'I am all about a lip, all the time. I just recently discovered the <em><a href="http://www.stilacosmetics.com/product/after+glow+lip+color.do" target="_blank">After Glow Lip Color</a></em> Crayons by Stila! Wearing Electric Pink above. They are a dream + come in five, you-need-them-all shades... <!--more--><a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/stilaafterglow1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-636" alt="stilaafterglow1" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/stilaafterglow1.jpg" width="3264" height="2176" /></a> <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/stilaafterglow2.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-637" alt="stilaafterglow2" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/stilaafterglow2.jpg" width="2619" height="1746" /></a>\r\n\r\nThese lip crayons give have a beautiful consistency, moisturizing + just the right amount of pigment, leaving your lips with the prettiest stain. Chunky crayon for easy application {poor Vivid Violet had a fall...} as well as great for on the go. Just remember when playing with color on your lips to moisturize + conceal around your mouth + nose for the maximum pop of color. Get to coloring! X', 'Makeup Musthave/ Stila After Glow Lip Color', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '634-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-01-28 06:17:59', '2015-01-28 06:17:59', '', 634, 'http://182.71.22.42/sarah/?p=2023', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
