(2056, 1, '2015-01-28 06:37:02', '2015-01-28 06:37:02', 'One of my favorite musicians to work with; Sleigh Bells. Alexis Krauss is such a bombshell. I love how she emotes darkness + has such an edge about her, yet is one of the loveliest gals I have ever worked with. Derek is amazing too + quirky + neurotic + crazy talented on so many levels. His 90''s playlists blow my mind. SO SO good. Â  <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/sb3.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-367" alt="SPIN-MARAPR-COVER-DP9.indd" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/sb3.jpg" width="650" height="449" /></a><!--more-->\r\n\r\nAlong with press events, we have shot for Spin, Clash, Paper + more. Can we also talk about their music. I am such a fan. <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/SB.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-369" alt="SB" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/SB.jpg" width="650" height="946" /></a><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-368" alt="sb2" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/sb2.jpg" width="650" height="508" /><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-366" alt="sb4" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/sb4.jpg" width="650" height="951" />\r\n\r\nIt''s a lot of eyeliner, structured brows + plump lips. Alexis'' hair is gorgeous, silky, healthy + easy to work with. Love the black against her fair, flawless skin.Â  She can do no wrong.<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-371" alt="SBCLASH3" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/SBCLASH3.jpg" width="335" height="450" /><a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/SBCLASH2.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-373" alt="SBCLASH2" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/SBCLASH2.jpg" width="715" height="450" /></a><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-372" alt="SBCLAS