(2057, 1, '2015-01-28 06:37:30', '2015-01-28 06:37:30', 'I am a huge fan of glowy, gorgeous, flawless skin [aren''t we all!]. Recently, I worked with talented Photographer Wendy Cassidy on a job, + in this post is model Amanda with her glowy creamy cheeks [These photos are unretouched!]! Of course amazing skin helps... Step by Step to get the rosy glow...<!--more-->\r\n\r\nâ€¢ LOVE YOUR SKIN WELL. You will always looks best when you are hydrated [H20!] + properly cleansing [YES, every AM+PM] + moisturizing generously.\r\n\r\nâ€¢ Get your foundation/tinted moisturizer etc. all over your face with your fingers or brushes, concealer on necessary areas for more coverage. You must take out all of the redness in order to make cheeks really pop + look intentional!\r\n\r\nâ€¢ If you want contoured cheeks for a more dramatic effect, apply a matte bronzer just below your cheekbones with a brush [I love <a href="http://www.essence.eu/us/usa/products/sun-club.html" target="_blank">Essence Sun Club Matte Bronzing Powder in Blonde</a>]\r\n\r\nâ€¢ Then using your fingers with the cream blush, dab product in a circular motion around the apples of your cheeks, blending up + out, diffusing the color toward the top of your cheekbones. [I love <a href="http://www.maccosmetics.com/product/shaded/156/15668/Products/Face/Cheek/Cremeblend-Blush/index.tmpl" target="_blank">MAC Cosmetics Cremeblend Blush in So Sweet</a>]\r\n\r\nâ€¢ Don''t be afraid if the color is not completely even! The very best trick to get it all blended + flawless is to use a touch of your foundation on a brush + blend around edges of cheek color to diffuse cheek color.\r\n\r\nâ€¢ I also love the cream blushes with a hint of shimmer in them, so fun in the summer to add that extra sheen!\r\n\r\nGet cheeky! X\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/Amanda61.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-395" alt="Amanda6" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/Amanda61.jpg" width="650" height="835" /></a>', 'How to: Creamy Pretty Cheeks', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '507-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-01-28 06:37:30', '2015-01-28 06:37:30', '', 507, 'http://182.71.22.42/sarah/?p=2057', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
