(2074, 1, '2015-01-28 07:03:24', '2015-01-28 07:03:24', '<p class="alignnone size-full wp-image-193">Dreamtown! Pun intended. Yesterday + today I teamed up with <a href="http://www.essence.eu/us/home.html" target="_blank">Essence Cosmetics</a> for desksides, [in my case, industry talk for visiting the fabulous beauty editors in NYC...]. If you aren''t familiar with the Essence, they are an incredible value brand out of Germany. If you are in the USA check out <a href="http://search.ulta.com/search?p=Q&amp;lbc=ulta&amp;uid=657721258&amp;ts=custom&amp;w=essence%20makeup&amp;method=and&amp;userid=Guest&amp;view=grid&amp;isort=date&amp;modaf=r:brand:essence" target="_blank">Ulta Beauty,</a> all you Canadians, Essence is readily available at Shoppers Drug Mart. I am a big fan of the line +Â  unlike most value brands, Essence has saturated color + pigment, staying power, + on trend products.</p>\r\n<!--more-->Â The days consisted of running between the Time+Life building, Conde Nast, Hearst, + more. It was so much fun to connect with the editors! Be sure to check out Essence''s Stays No Matter What collection launching in the next two weeks. My favorite: Stays No Matter What eye pencil in black. This Spring, get into it! S.\r\n<p class="alignnone size-full wp-image-193"><a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/3.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-191" alt="3" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/3.jpg" width="1188" height="1701" /></a> <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/photo-2.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-192" alt="photo 2" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/photo-2.jpg" width="2448" height="3264" /></a></p>', 'Desksides, the Essence of...', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '495-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-01-28 07:03:24', '2015-01-28 07:03:24', '', 495, 'http://182.71.22.42/sarah/?p=2074', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
