(2247, 1, '2015-02-09 10:37:35', '2015-02-09 10:37:35', '<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/2015_CAUDALIE_EYE_SWOON_PUTNAM_FLOWERS_02.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1875" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/2015_CAUDALIE_EYE_SWOON_PUTNAM_FLOWERS_02.jpg" alt="2015_CAUDALIE_EYE_SWOON_PUTNAM_FLOWERS_02" width="1856" height="1223" /></a>Â The end of last week I found myself in the <a href="http://us.caudalie.com/?gclid=Cj0KEQiA3bymBRC19IrD7O_NrYsBEiQAb2dpA9O3XeHt8UeCVdgFPibgXZy56DnnjOe7Klb6o8hnv5YaArcI8P8HAQ" target="_blank">Caudalie </a>boutique in the West Village, amidst some of my very favorite things . Sipping the delicious wine from Mathilde''s Vineyard in France, we indulged in food all sourced from ingredients that Caudalie uses in their skin care; grapes, lemon, pear, coriander. Founders of Caudalie, Mathilde + Bertrand spoke about their newest product, ''the rolls royce'' of facial serums, <a href="http://us.caudalie.com/premier-cru-elixir.html" target="_blank">Premier Cru The Elixir</a>...<!--more-->\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1885" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/2015_CAUDALIE_EYE_SWOON_PUTNAM_FLOWERS_ELIXIR_10.jpg" alt="2015_CAUDALIE_EYE_SWOON_PUTNAM_FLOWERS_ELIXIR_10" width="2172" height="1041" />Poppy''s Catering is my favorite in NYC, they source local as much as possible + have amazing taste, quite literally. Not only are all of the bites delicious, but they look beautiful too...<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/2015_CAUDALIE_EYE_SWOON_PUTNAM_FLOWERS_ELIXIR_06.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1879" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/2015_CAUDALIE_EYE_SWOON_PUTNAM_FLOWERS_ELIXIR_06.jpg" alt="2015_CAUDALIE_EYE_SWOON_PUTNAM_FLOWERS_ELIXIR_06" width="2208" height="1248" /></a> Mathilde Thomas speaking about the properties + performance of <a href="http://us.caudalie.com/premier-cru-elixir.html" target="_blank">The Elixir</a>. Lifestyle blogger + interior genius, Athena Calderone from <a href="http://eye-swoon.com/" target="_blank">Eye Swoon</a> co-hosted the event.<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1877" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/2015_CAUDALIE_EYE_SWOON_PUTNAM_FLOWERS_ELIXIR_01.jpg" alt="2015_CAUDALIE_EYE_SWOON_PUTNAM_FLOWERS_ELIXIR_01" width="1919" height="926" />Â Â  <a href="http://www.poppyscatering.com/" target="_blank">Poppy''s Catering</a> made a delicious grape + meyer lemon jelly.<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/2015_CAUDALIE_EYE_SWOON_PUTNAM_FLOWERS_ELIXIR_EVENT_04.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1880" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/2015_CAUDALIE_EYE_SWOON_PUTNAM_FLOWERS_ELIXIR_EVENT_04.jpg" alt="2015_CAUDALIE_EYE_SWOON_PUTNAM_FLOWERS_ELIXIR_EVENT_04" width="2208" height="1248" /></a>Â  The new power Premier Cru duo! <a href="http://us.caudalie.com/premier-cru-elixir.html" target="_blank">The Elixir</a> is a beautiful product that is half oil + half serum. The formula is silicon free + anti-aging + when used under the Premier Cru, <a href="http://us.caudalie.com/premier-cru-the-cream-2.html" target="_blank">The Cream,</a> will leave your skin soft, supple + plump. After using it for a couple of months [love a preview of a good product!], I find it is enhancing my moisturizer, really locking in all of the moisture.<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/2015_CAUDALIE_EYE_SWOON_PUTNAM_FLOWERS_ELIXIR_EVENT_08.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1882" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/2015_CAUDALIE_EYE_SWOON_PUTNAM_FLOWERS_ELIXIR_EVENT_08.jpg" alt="2015_CAUDALIE_EYE_SWOON_PUTNAM_FLOWERS_ELIXIR_EVENT_08" width="2208" height="1248" /></a> Mathilde + Bertrand + Alix, my dear friend + designer of French Women''s line, <a href="http://heimstone.com/" target="_blank">Heimstone,</a> enjoying the vino.<a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/2015_CAUDALIE_EYE_SWOON_PUTNAM_FLOWERS_HEIMSTONE_09.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1883" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/2015_CAUDALIE_EYE_SWOON_PUTNAM_FLOWERS_HEIMSTONE_09.jpg" alt="2015_CAUDALIE_EYE_SWOON_PUTNAM_FLOWERS_HEIMSTONE_09" width="2208" height="1248" /></a> <a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/2015_CAUDALIE_EYE_SWOON_SMITH_HAVT_LAFITTE_03.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1884" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/2015_CAUDALIE_EYE_SWOON_SMITH_HAVT_LAFITTE_03.jpg" alt="2015_CAUDALIE_EYE_SWOON_SMITH_HAVT_LAFITTE_03" width="2208" height="1248" /></a><a href="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/2015_CAUDALIE_EYE_SWOON_PUTNAM_FLOWERS_05.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1876" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/2015_CAUDALIE_EYE_SWOON_PUTNAM_FLOWERS_05.jpg" alt="2015_CAUDALIE_EYE_SWOON_PUTNAM_FLOWERS_05" width="2208" height="1248" /></a> I was sent home with one of the bouquets! Being a flower girl that loves to have fresh flowers in my home, this was a treat. Flower Masters of the best Floral shop in NYC, Matthew + Derek co-founders of <a href="http://putnamflowers.com/" target="_blank">Putnam+Putnam</a>, put together the most beautiful arrangements. <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1881" src="http://sarahappleby.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/2015_CAUDALIE_EYE_SWOON_PUTNAM_FLOWERS_ELIXIR_EVENT_07.jpg" alt="2015_CAUDALIE_EYE_SWOON_PUTNAM_FLOWERS_ELIXIR_EVENT_07" width="1983" height="1179" />I need a lot more of all of this in my life! A delicious evening indeed... X', 'LIVE/ A nite with CAUDALIE X EYE SWOON X PUTNAM FLOWERS X POPPY''S', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2245-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-02-09 10:37:35', '2015-02-09 10:37:35', '',